product_title: Easy Tool Stainless Steel Fruit Pineapple Corer Slicer Peeler Cut (One size, sliver)
review_headline: ★ THESE REALLY DO WORK GREAT WITH SOME TWEAKING ★
review_body:
These Really Do Work Great, But You Do Need To Know a Few Things. I've Been Using Mine For a Few Years Now. First, I Paid a Few Dollars Less For Mine and The Price Has Jumped. They're All Imported, so Try to Find Either a Cheaper One or One That's Extremely Well Made. This One is Made Well Enough, If You're Careful. This Thing Can Cut You, So Don't Let Some Kid Use It, "Because It Looks Like Fun!!" You Need A Pineapple That's Big Enough. I Can't Tell You How Many Times I Went to Wal-Mart or the Grocery Store and Their Pineapples were Just Too Small of a Diameter. It HAS to Be Big Enough. It's Better To Have Some Waste on The Inside Of The Husk.

When I'm Finished Using The Pineapple Corer, Then I Cut Up the Husk Of The Pineapple To Get The Rest Of The Pineapple Cut Up and I Save The Core of the Pineapple To Go Into My Iced Tea Pitcher or Drink Pitcher (That's How They Do It In Hawaii) When I Was In Hawaii, They Never Threw Away The Core, They Always Used It For Something. Sometimes, They Even Grilled It, Although I've Never Tried That. But, I Know They Did It With Honey and Some Kind of Teriyaki People Have Also Left Chunks of Pineapple on the Husk and Grilled it Meat Side Down on the Grill. Then, They Eat The Chunks of Grilled Pineapple and Use The Husks Like a Little Bowl.. You Don't Grill The Husk Part. You Can Also Keep The Husk Whole, Like a Bowl and Take the Center Core Out, Then Fill It Full Of Fruit Salad or Use it as a Drink Container or Dessert Container.

Someone Told Me They Like To Make Pineapple Greek Yogurt and Fill It, Then Freeze It a Short Time. I've Never Tried That. I've Made Pineapple Cheesecake and That's Delicious, but I Know It's Tricky Working With Pineapple Sometimes. You Know, If You've Ever Tried to Make Jello & Put Pineapple In. YIKES!!! The Bromelain in the Pineapple Keeps Your Gelatin From Setting. It is a Great Anti-Inflammatory & Helps Your Digestive Tract & Tummy Feel Better, But That Same Enzyme Interferes with Your Jello Setting Up.

When Washing These, Be Extra Carful and Wash Them Separate. I Use Tooth Picks, to Get the Pineapple Out That Gets Stuck In The Little Crevices. I Always Put The Parts Back Into The Box & Make Sure Everything is Dry. So, That's It. Make Sure Your Pineapple is Big Enough. Get All Your Pineapple To Work For You. Clean Your Corer and Protect Your Hands. That's It. Thank You For Reading.Same Enzyme Interferes with Your Jello Setting Up.

When Washing These, Be Extra Carful and Wash Them Separate. I Use Tooth Picks, to Get the Pineapple Out That Gets Stuck In The Little Crevices. I Always Put The Parts Back Into The Box & Make Sure Everything is Dry. So, That's It. Make Sure Your Pineapple is Big Enough. Get All Your Pineapple To Work For You. Clean Your Corer and Protect Your Hands. That's It. Thank You For Reading.

product_title: RFID Blocking Stylish Genuine Leather Wallet for Men - Excellent as Travel Bifold
review_body: I received the RFID Blocking Leather Wallet. The first thing I noticed is the pebbled texture and it's very soft. I love the flip out window which makes showing your identification quick and convenient...don't have to worry about leaving your id behind! Also, the navy blue stripe patterns inside the billfold section is a nice touch. There are 8 credit card slots to pack your plastic! It's a slim design, nothing bulky here. Of course, the RFID protection built into the wallet is the best feature. Nice not to worry about scanning devices or wireless identity theft.

product_title: RFID Blocking Stylish Genuine Leather Wallet for Men - Excellent as Travel Bifold
review_headline: Roomy and soft to the touch
review_body:
I love this wallet. The first thing I noticed is how soft and flexible it is. Most wallets tend to be a bit stiff, even when they are completely empty. This one is flexible enough that it is more comfortable to keep in my pocket than most wallets. The leather itself is soft and has a pebbled texture to it.

The wallet is also nice to look at. The lining inside is black and white striped, which I thought was a bit interesting, but it grew on me pretty quickly. The edges of the wallet aren't at all rough and the seams are all well done.

This wallet has plenty of room to hold everything I need to put in it. I also really like having two spots for for cash or papers in the back. I like being able to keep my cash separate from anything else and that isn't possible with some wallets. The RFID blocking is a great additional feature that I really appreciate.

I love this wallet for myself, but it is also a great wallet for gifting.

I received this item at a discount in exchange for my honest review.

product_title: Steampunk Victorian Costume Ulysses Side-Button Linen Shirt [Orange]
review_headline: It's actually very comfortable and breathable.  The shipping was unbelievably fast.
review_body: I ordered this to wear at a Con in Atlanta and was worried it was going to be too hot to wear.  I was expecting the fabric to be thick and stiff.  It's actually very comfortable and breathable.  It's a mix between cotton and linen much like the shirts I wear in the Florida heat so I don't expect to have to worry about heat exhaustion even though it's long sleeved.  I will update after the Con on how well it performs.  The fit is a bit looser than I expected but that's actually a good thing in my case.  I have a 48" chest and ordered the X-Large according to the size chart.  I was expecting the shirt to come out a bit small for me as I am very overweight and my gut definitely exceeds my chest size.  The shirt is actually a little loose on me.  The sleeves were too long for me but that's normal for me.  When you have to order larger sizes because you are overweight, the arm length increases as well.  If you have this same problem, you can re-sew the button for the cuff to make the cuff size smaller.  That will make the cuff stop when it touches the top of your hand instead of hanging down over your hand.  I almost forgot:  They shipped amazingly fast.  I was expecting this to take nearly a week without Prime shipping and was worried it might not arrive before the convention next week.   Amazingly, it arrived at the same time as the Amazon Prime items I ordered along with it.

product_title: Nolama Women's Powernet Body Shaper Firm Control Bodysuit Shapewear
review_headline: Showing off my fabulous curves with no bulges...
review_body:
This is my new favorite body shaper! I've tried all sorts of these waist cinchers and shapers recently, and I can honestly tell you that I was a little leery about accepting one more free sample. But, when I was offered the chance to review this one, I knew I had to try it for one main reason -- the zipper! All the rest of the ones I've tried have been hook and eye or tie up, and those were tedious to get in and out of. Some have ribs that dug into my skin, and although most made me look great, they were often uncomfortable and I had difficulty sitting and bending in them. Not this one! Made of a nice stretchy material, it also has a very soft interior, and I got mine in the beige color. As far as size, I ordered the XXL even though it was a little bigger than I need according to the handy chart on the product page.

What I really love about this body shaper -- it's smooth, and one piece, with a hook and eye closure at the bottom in the crotch area so it fits quite tight and everything gets compressed evenly. It is advertised to take 2 to 4 inches off your waist, and it really does. Because of the zipper, there are no little bulges when worn under clothing. I also like the fact that it has shoulder straps that lift your bust and also compress it a bit from both sides, evenly, to really enhance the look and even defy a bit of gravity! So put on your sexiest bra, zip yourself into this well tailored body shaper, and put on your favorite outfit to look slimmer -- and feel comfortable while looking fabulous.

I'd recommend this most enthusiastically and definitely prefer it to the waist corsets and shapers. Try it, you'll see!

product_title: Alain Dupetit Men’s Two Button TR Blend Suit in Many Colors
review_headline: the suit was in excellent form right out of the box and was ready ...
review_body: After seeing the only suit buried in my closet that I never wear, my girlfriend said to me, “We’re going to my parents’ 30th wedding anniversary party, not their funeral or a job interview.” So I asked her to find me a new one, something inexpensive, because I’ll only wear it once.  She said she ordered a charcoal grey one by Alain Dupetit, which we’d never heard of before.  The package arrived promptly, but I didn’t bother to take the suit out until the day of the party. Much to my surprise, the suit was in excellent form right out of the box and was ready to be worn without ironing, and the fabric felt nice to the touch. My girlfriend also commented on how nicely it fit me, as if it were tailored.  When my girlfriend and I arrived at the party, her parents told me I looked “really handsome” (something this critical duo had never said to me before). But that’s not just it. Later when I was getting food at the buffet a woman—someone way out of my league—came up to me, asked me for my name and wanted to see if I wanted to get out of the party with her and go swimming in the hotel pool. WTF?! Mind you, this kind of thing NEVER happens to me. I’m not fugly, but I’m no Christian Grey. At first I thought I misunderstood her heavily accented English, but then she repeated it again slowly, enunciating each word. Before I could get out of my shock and say anything, my girlfriend came over and introduced me to that attractive woman (her mother’s distant cousin’s daughter visiting from France). That experience made me truly understand the phrase “clothes make the man” and realize you don’t have to spend a fortune to look like a million bucks.  I'm definitely going to order more suits from this brand.

product_title: Pay Off Your Hard Work These Smart, Classy, and Trendy Work Dresses for Women
review_headline: Cute dress, a little short.. but super cute!
review_body:
I am super careful when ordering clothes online and make sure that I check the sizing chart a couple of times before making my selection.

When this dress arrived, my daughter was excited to put it right on. Sadly, it was bigger than expected in the arm openings and shorter in the length. However, she likes the dress and that is half the battle with teens. So she is going to wear it with leggings which takes care of the length issue. For the arm openings, she will wear a dark tank while it is still warm outside and then a light sweater once the temps start to fall.

Other than the sizing difference, we both like the dress. The top is form fitting while the skirt is free flowing. It "swishes" as she walks which is apparently a good thing to teen girls. Go figure!

I left our rating as a 5 since the dress is well made and is super cute. The sizing issue was one we were able to work around.

Promotional or discounted product provided for review.

review_headline: Great head cover forthe house ad out
review_body:
My aunt is going through treatments right now for the third time. She lives in Florida, so it is often to hot for her to wear a wig all the time. She often goes around with nothing because it is more comfortable. She mentioned that at times it is awkward when people stare. I jumped at the chance to review these items because it is something she can really use!

Great soft material that hugs your head! I really like the elastic piece at back to hold longer hair. This allows my aunt to use this later when her hair grows in as well. It is a light weight material, so it should not be too hot in Florida. It is a great way for her to cover her head and not feel so awkward. She can also attach her bangs piece to the front!

If she is ok with taking pictures I will ad them, for now you have to settle for photos of me in them.

product_title: Nolama Women's Shapewear Firm Control High-Waist Thigh Slimmer Waist Cincher
review_body:
Sometimes, I feel self conscious. I've lost 140+lbs, and kept it off for the past 5 years.Even though I'm considerably thinner. and do love my body, I was left with a bit of loose skin around my abdomen. For the most part, it's easily concealed.
There are times I want to wear more form fitting dresses or bodysuits, and don't want lumps & bumps to show.
That's when I depend on Shape Wear to help. I've tried tons of brands + styles. I ordered this in hopes of improving my curves, and suppressing the trouble areas.
I received the package within a day and a half! Minutes of snagging it from my mailbox, I rushed to my bedroom to try it on.
I was blown away by how easy it was to get into. It only took maybe 2 minutes (if that) to completely latch the hooks and zip up. In the past, I've struggled~this one is super easy to get into. The zipper locks into place, and the silicone around the top, fully holds it up.
The fabric is soft, feels lightweight and easy to breathe and move around in. It Lifts, Tones + Cinches in ALL the Right Areas:
*It gave me a much smaller waist
*smoothed the area around my bra line
*lifted my backside
*toned my thighs
and was like an "instant tummy tuck", without the pain & downtime!!
*I probably should've ordered a size or two smaller. Though. it does fit well, nonetheless. For future reference, this is true to size*
I'm thoroughly impressed with this longline, high waisted piece. It's study and exceptionally well made. I love the high quality, firm, stretchy 'control fabric' that effortlessly gives the illusion of an hourglass figure.
Just putting it on improves my confidence level. Wearing it out? I feel stunning and am pleased with my "new figure"!!
I highly recommend giving this a try. It's unusual to find shape wear that is comfy, and still contours.
*i received this product at a reduced price in exchange for my honest, unbiased opinion.

review_body:
I ordered the "Raglan Flutter Sleeve Women Casual Dress."
I'm 5'5" with a longer torso vs legs. I followed the pictured size chart (not Amazon's, you'll likely order a dress that's too small if you use their standard size chart here), took my measurements, and the dress fits as expected. This dress sits at my natural waist and the hemline is right around my knees. The material is thin, but opaque (black dress). It is also soft and comfortable. My only quibble is that the material does pick up some lint/pet hair that was not difficult to remove. I received this dress at a discounted price in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

Update: The fit is flattering and I have received many compliments on this dress.

product_title: Adorable Dresses for Women for a Casual Yet Distinctive Style
review_body:

I actually ordered it for my 10 year old, since we've been looking for some flowy black dresses for some concept photographer shoots we're planning. She is 54" tall and 100 pounds. I attempted to order the Extra Small but it was out of stock and I went with the Small. I'm glad I did, since it fits, but not with a lot of room to spare. She's a little chunky so I hope as she grows taller, the dress will still fit. It's difficult to find dresses for little girls who are outgrowing children's sizes (in the bust) but are still not developed enough for juniors' sizes. This dress is conservative enough. The neckline is a little deep on her but a think black undershirt/tank correct that issue. The material is very soft, silky and stretchy and ultimately, she loves the dress.

I received this item at a discount in exchange for sharing my honest, unbiased review.

review_body:

The size is in between "true to size" and "slightly smaller". If you're in between sizes, order one size up. However, if you're true to your size, I feel like ordering your true size will be fine. Depends on how you want it to fit. I'm a bit fuller on the chest, so I ordered a size up. And it fits nice, I think. The dress is a bit too short for my liking (I'm 5'4"), but wearing a leggings would solve the problem. Overall, it's a cute dress, and it's something I'll wear a lot.

I received a discount on the dress for my honest opinion. My review above is 100% unbiased.

product_title: Women White and Gold Dresses under $25 for all Occasion
review_body:
I got the Gold Rings of Rose and it's absolutely beautiful. It kind of reminds me of a Flapper dress from the 20's. In my dress buying experience on Amazon so far, it seems like many sellers are from China. Sometimes it can make getting the right size kind of tricky. They have the size chart on this listing - but I don't believe it's correct. I am 5' 5" and about 120 lbs. If I were shopping locally with a US dressmaker, I'd usually get a size 4. If I follow the size chart in this listing, that would be a small. But suspecting this might be a dress from China, I ordered the medium. It is a perfect fit. If you are a similar size to me, definitely get a medium. Just thought I'd want to mention that, as not everyone will know the sizing issue. What I mean by a perfect fit is it's not tight or restrictive - and yet it doesn't look frumpy or too big. It is about 1" above my knee and is figure flattering.

This is a more mature dress. I'd say it's for a mature adult woman rather than a teenager. The colors are rich. It has style. This dress is 100% polyester. I love that. I just had my cat jump in my lap and no hairs are sticking. This is one reason I love polyester, that, and it's wrinkle resistant, and you can wash it a million times and it still looks good. It also has a vibrant purple built-in slip under the outer dress - so it's not too sheer​. This would be a nice dress to wear to church or out to dinner. I received this dress at a discount in exchange for an honest, unbiased product review. All opinions expressed are truly my own. Very pretty and would recommend!

product_title: EROIX Underneathwear Mens Boardroom Underwear
review_body:
I’ve been stuck on the same boxers for years. The Eroix intrigued me because of the lack of a stretchy waist band. I’ve now switched allegiances to Eroix. The only thing better is going commando.
The pro’s are :
1) They just fit at just the right spot on your hips and stay there. You’re not packing a parachute down every once in a while with the stretch band style.
2) They’re a little shorter then normal boxers which just feel better. The leg holes give you plenty of room so they’re still comfortable too.
3) The quality on these are great. I didnt know I cared about how well my underwear were made but these make me feel like I’m wearing something special.
4) My wife really digs them.
This brings me to the cons;
I end up wearing my underwear around the house all the time now since they feel like I have a pair of board shorts on.
Pick up a couple of pair to try, you wont be disappointed.

product_title: EROIX Underneathwear Mens Suit & Tied Underwear
review_headline: I love the button up style and tailored fit of the ...
review_body:
After receiving my first order of multiple pairs in both styles a couple month ago, I can say that they are the first pair of underwear I go for after laundry day.

I love the button up style and tailored fit of the Boardrooms, but I find there is something unexpected and unique about tieing up my Suit & Tied underwear that I really enjoy. They look awesome and feel great!

I like the material because it seems to dry fast and breathe well. I have not traveled to different countries with them yet but I could see how they would be great to have on a backpacking or camping trip. I also feel that the fit on the waist is spot on. I tend to wear a 31 in the waist, and with other brands the sizing can vary. When I put on my Eroixs they fit me perfectly, the sizing is spot on.

It’s nice to have a new alternative to mens underwear.

Thanks EROIX! Looking forward to seeing what you all do next.

product_title: Zoozie LA Women's Racerback Maxi Dress Sleeveless
review_body: I am living in maxi dresses now that I just delivered a few months ago and my body isn't exactly fitting into all of my pre pregnancy clothes.  Nothing is more devastating then putting on my favorite pair of jeans, jumping around the house trying to get them to zip and button up, and they just wont, at least not yet.  I like the femininity of a maxi dress, with the comfort of not squeezing my waist into something and making myself look larger than I really am with a muffin top.  I was a bit nervous with this maxi dress since its horizontal stripes that would make me appear larger than I am.  Regardless, I love maxi dresses and figured I'd try it and maybe when I lost more weight I'd love it more.  So the dress arrives and like a kid on Christmas morning, I rush to my room to try it on right away, it fit me perfectly.  I have a large bust of 38D/DD, so dresses don't always fit me as I'd like them to in the bust area.  the maxi dress is so comfortable and thick unlike many dresses I've bought that were too tight and so thin that they were almost see through.  The dress is beautiful, soft and casual yet elegant.  Now my only con with this dress is that it comes to my ankles.  I normally like my maxi dresses to fall to my feel but this one doesn't, but I presume that due to my large bust that it possible rides up a bit higher than an average busted woman's dress would.  Now just because its at my ankles doesn't mean its not just as beautiful and elegant, it actually will keep it from ripping at the bottom, and I can also show off some cute sandals with it.  This dress is perfect for spring, summer, or fall pairing it with a cute jean jacket or something for the cooler nights.  I got the Navy and Teal striped dress and the colors are beautiful.  The stitching is done to perfection, with no loose threads.  I love the material of the dress that is 49% polyester, 48% rayon, and 3% spandex. I presume this would shrink in the dryer and since its already a bit short on me, I hand washed mine and hung dried it as the care tag suggested or this can also be dry cleaned.  I love this dress and wore it to my nephews birthday party this past weekend and received many compliments on how beautiful the dress is and how slimming it is on me, exactly what every new mom wants to hear!  Promotional discount provided in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

I am in between a small and medium.  I am 5'4 126 lbs and I choose the small.  It is such a great fit and length.  I love the scoop neck line and the racerback back.  You can easily wear a racerback or strapless bra.  The seam down the back of the dress is very flattering on your backside. I will get a ton of use out of this dress.  I plan on wearing it the rest of summer and throwing  a denim  jacket over it in the fall. I did receive this at a promotional discount for my honest unbiased review.  I love it so much I will be purchasing another one.

I prefer it to a regular bra because the straps don't dig in or slip off my shoulders, the band doesn't dig in, there are no itchy tags, and it supports my bust without flattening it. bottom band: 12.25"

review_body: My daughter though 2 years old wears 3T dresses because of her height, she is half inch short to be 3 feet. The removable bow/ flower has a safety pin attached on the back so you can decide where you want it, I liked it the way it is shown in the picture. review_body:
This was received for free or at a discount for my honest thoughts and review. All thoughts are my own and no other's. This review is in the guidelines of the FTC.

This shirt is not just an election shirt, it's a piece of history, a Novelty. Anything that can be a piece of history, I'm interested in. I love things that tell a story of something that happened a long time ago. It's like something you can sit on the front porch with your parents or grandparents and listen to stories of when they were small. I miss those days. Now I share stories with my children. review_body: So here is the deal...a complimentary sample of these were included in another order from this same company. It is not normally a style that MrJavajunki would normally wear - to put it mildly. In the decades of being together, I've never seen him wear anything remotely like these. Being an old-school sort, he calls these "man panties" and seemed to alternate between insulted and suspicious when I suggested he give them a try. Because these are not his norm, this review is based solely and exclusively on the quality of the material and workmanship. These are made from bamboo which seems like an odd material at first but which makes a lot of sense - it's cool and breaths a lot like cotton but is tougher. These are well made, can be tossed directly into the washing machine without worry and while MrJavajunki isn't personally very comfortable due to the style, these fit the way they are intended to fit (go one size up due to Asian sizing versus US). review_headline: Very lovely dress, both the color and the fit are fabulous.
review_body: I am LOVING this dress!  The cut is absolutely phenomenal.  Everything about this dress screams quality.  I was hoping that when I tried on the dress that I would love it just as much as I fell in love with the advertisement photo, but since I can be quite picky with my clothing I wasn't holding my breath.  Taking it out of the package, I noticed right away that the fabric used in the manufacturing of this dress was good quality.  It is a somewhat thick and heavy fabric that has a nice stretch to it.  The robin egg blueish color is one of my favorites and was one of the reasons I was so excited to receive this.  The dress was true to color, I was thrilled about that.  I love the length which is just at the top of my knee.  I am 5 feet tall so it may end up a tad shorter on someone of a more standard height.  The fabric falls beautifully, and I really fell in love with the seams of this dress.  there are seams that go down the bust of the dress in the front which make this a very well fitting dress.  The waistline is nice and high and the skirt flows beautifully.  The off the shoulder cut is fantastic!  It looks lovely.  This is a very nice and comfortably fitting dress.  Since I struggle between a medium and a large I went ahead and ordered this in large and I am glad I did.  Great fit.  I received this product at a discounted rate in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Womens Summer Chiffon Bohemian Floral Printed Full Length Maxi Dress
review_headline: Beautiful dress but COMPLETLY see through
review_body:
Let me start off by saying that this dress is absolutely gorgeous and high quality. The detailing and stitching is precise and accurate. A very high quality item indeed. HOWEVER, the whole dress is entirely see through. The skirt is made with a sheer chiffon like material that can be remedied by wearing a slip. The from and back of the top would be okay if you wear a white bra otherwise you could see the color of your bra. The sides are crocheted so that's not covering anything. Solutions to this would be to wear a white bandeau top or tank and a slip BUT it is a summer dress and I do not want to have to layer all those clothes, that is why I only gave it 3 stars. I am not sure if I am keeping this dress so I have not washed it and cannot say how it holds up after wear.

product_title: Ekouaer Sleepwear Womens Chemise Nightgown Full Slip Lace Lounge Dress
review_body:
I passed along this woman's sleepwear to my wife who wrote the following about it:

"The Ekouaer Womens nightgown I received in exchange for an honest review consists of a long camisole slip style that is made of a soft cotton like material. The nightgown is trimmed on the bodice with a very pretty lace. The nightgown is sexy but sweet and provided me with both comfort and style. I enjoyed wearing and reviewing this beautiful nightgown."

product_title: Ekouaer Sleepwear Womens Chemise Nightgown Full Slip Lace Lounge Dress
review_headline: well-made and comfortable; useful to me as a slip
review_body:
I have this in black, size medium. It's pretty stretchy fabric so I probably could've gone down a size and still had it fit. (I have several items from Ekouaer and their sizing has been getting better and better for the US market.)

This is cute and well-made (no loose seams, holes, threads sticking out, etc.). I'm using it as a slip beneath black/dark skirts that are a little too sheer for comfort. The fabric is dyed evenly (and the fabric has a really nice feel to it) and the lace details are cute.

Note on the bra size -- I am a B cup and if you are going to wear this without a separate bra, you would probably not want to be any bigger than a B cup or you might spill out. It doesn't have any built-in support. That's not a bad thing, and it's fairly evident from the images, I think, but it is just something to keep in mind. (It does provide adequate coverage for me, though.)

I'm going to hand wash this to keep it nice. It does have a washing instructions label but it is all in symbols (I never remember what they mean) instead of words. So I figure hand washing is safe. Overall, a nice product that definitely fit a need I had.

Product provided by the seller for evaluation purposes.

product_title: Ekouaer Sleepwear Womens Chemise Nightgown Full Slip Lace Lounge Dress
review_body:
These are my wife’s comments on the nightgown. This nightgown (navy color) is very cute with its design and seems to be well made with quality material that is sewn together well. The navy is a nice color as well. The nightgown is comfortable to wear with its soft, breathable material. This medium size fits as it should as she normally wears a medium in this type of clothing. product_title: TaichiPanda® Women's Cotton Low Rise Trunk Sexy Underwear Briefs (One size, Rose2)
review_headline: I love the color of these
review_body:
I love the color of these, it is a beautiful bright pink. The lace is very nice, delicate but not to much where it will rip easily. They have a decent amount of stretch and the initial stiffness should soften with use and wash. They are one size fits all, but the tag states Medium, and they seem a bit small even for a medium. If they had a tad more stretch to them it may be a little more suitable to say one size fits all. The fit is nice, they arent as high as a regular hi-cut bikini in the leg but dont ride right in the crease of the leg either. The rise is agood with a low-rise jean. They do have a reasonable amount of give in the butt, however if you've got a "booty" expect them to be slightly snug, and they seem to ride up the cheek a bit, which is acceptable and expected.

I received this product for free in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: TaichiPanda® Women's Cotton Low Rise Trunk Sexy Underwear Briefs (One size, Rose2)
review_body: I did hand wash them right away, in cool water, as I do with all clothing items I buy or receive. I hung them to dry and they dried fairly quickly. As soon as I put them on I loved them! These sexy low rise trunk undies are exactly that, sexy! They came in a size medium which is what I originally wear. I like them to not be so big in the back, and these were just that. The front covers as much as the picture in the items description shows. It is a very comfortable cotton low rise underwear and the color I got was Rose2. I can only imagine that they look just as sexy in all the colors available! Being 5' 7", 135 pounds and hips are a 39", the low rise trunks do rise up on your booty. They rise up half way around the booty like a Rio look. It is comfortable because the fabric has a nice stretch to it and the lace is not bothersome at all. These do not fall in the crease of your leg, they go slightly above it. That way you don't feel any uncomfortable friction while wearing them. They won't rip easily either thanks to the nice makeup of the materials used. I appreciate the opportunity to receive this item for free for my honest and unbiased review.

review_headline: I really love the SlimMe style
review_body: I really love the MeMoi style shaper. I've bought the Flexees before and find the MeMoi far better for controlling my bulges! They look great under my white slacks. The inseam is 14 inches when purchased. That shrinks down an inch or so after washing ,but will stretch out again.  When I wear one under polyester slacks and my inner thighs rub together, shapers can cause my slacks to ride up due to static created by the rubbing. But Static Guard solved that issue and now my slacks and skirts flow over my shapers with no problem.. They are opaque. Also they don't pill, snag, or run. They are very durable and wash well-keeping their shaping properties. I just bought 7 more because they are quite comfortable and not too hot during summer days. They are also affordably priced..

product_title: PLATN Men's Heavy Plate Copper Minimalist Wallet
review_headline: Brilliant, simple wallet design that is built for life.
review_body:
This Wallet is cleverly designed and easy to use. The o'rings fit perfectly in place and firmly keep the two pieces together. The O'rings are replaceable too making the the wallet itself built for life. I have managed to get over half an inch stack inside without any issues and I have used it on nights out with just license and some cash. In both cases I found it to be comfortable to carry and easy to use. The Copper has a lush heavy feel and the look is amazing. It is defiantly the only wallet anyone has ever complemented me on.

The lack of branding, the excellent design and the beautiful aesthetic together make for a unique item that stands out from run of the mill wallets. Considering I usually destroy my leather wallets every other year or so I am looking forward to saving money in the future with this item that should last me the rest of my life.

product_title: Meaneor Women's Oversized Open Longline Sleeveless Duster Blazer Jacket Coat
review_body: This is a very pretty blazer!  The fabric that it is made of is so beautiful, soft and silky.  It is a great fall accessory paired with a sweater, jeans and boots!  The stitching is beautifully done throughout the piece and it is well constructed.  I received this blazer in white and the color is stunning.  It has an elegant feel about it and the fabric flows beautifully.  This blazer is adorned with two pockets, one on either side.  They are nice sized pockets if you were to actually need to use them.  The length is somewhat long, it comes down on my to about my mid thigh, although I am only 5 feet tall so I would imagine most people it wouldn't be so long on.  I felt like the blazer was a little smaller around than it should have been and the fit was a little awkward for me around the front of the blazer.  I thought that the front should have come a little closer together and I think that I would have felt a little more comfortable if it had.  But it's a beautiful piece of clothing and for someone a little less curvy or if you go up a size from what you think you would need it would probably be a better fit for you.  I received this product complimentary in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Meaneor Women's Oversized Open Longline Sleeveless Duster Blazer Jacket Coat
review_headline: Flowy design adds a nice element of fashion to an outfit, although the fit is a bit smaller than I expected
review_body:
When I saw this sleeveless blazer from Meaneor, I was quite intrigued, thinking that it wasn't like anything else in my wardrobe, so I was excited to give it a try. Just as the description says, it is a blazer style jacket, with a standard blazer lapel, but without sleeves. I like the long flowy design. The description says that the fabric is stretchy, but I really don't feel much "give" to the fabric and wish it had a bit more elasticity, although the fabric does have a nice, soft feel. I ordered a size Large, which is what I would typically wear and it is a bit small. I'm not sure if it is intended to be able to close all the way across the front of the chest and abdomen (there are no buttons or other closures), but for me it is a bit tight to try to have the two sides meet up and the armholes are also slightly small. Still just as an open long vest, it looks stylish and adds an interesting fashionable note to my outfit.

I'm very glad that I was able to order this as a free promotional sample in order to evaluate and provide my honest review.

product_title: Bepei Women's Long Sleeves One Button Open Front Wraps Soft Cardigan Sweater
review_body: [[VIDEOID:a318d6724e97914ed473de52f5183cfa]]I tend to be more modest than most women my age.  The problem with that is that I have a large bust.  Most items for my age tend to show off a lot of cleavage. I also have the problem of getting cold really easy.    I have to say I was so excited by the color options for this.  How is it possible to choose just one color?  I went with black because it goes with everything.    I ordered the XXL because I like things to be a little big to allow for the bust. I have to say that there is more than enough room and that makes me so happy.    I love the one button closure on this because it allows for breathing room for my girls (aka my bust).  The button is pretty as well, just the perfect size for this.    This is made of a stretch material and is very comfortable. You would think that with this certain being so thin that it would not keep you warm but it really does keep me warm.  At the same time it does not over heat me at all, I swear it is just the right combo of cooling and insulating.    Even with it unbutton it still allows me to be modest when I need to be.    I have to say that I am so in love with this Cardigan it's not funny. I love to wear it around my house because I live in Texas and the ac has to be pretty much running all the time to keep the house cool.    I hope that you are just as happy with yours as I am mine (if you can decide on the color lol)    I did get this product for free in exchange for my honest review. I am not compensated in any way for this review.

product_title: Exceptional Coats for Women That Are Perfect for Fall and Winter
review_headline: Super cute printed lightweight jacket perfect for fall!
review_body:
This is a great lightweight coat for fall and prints are huge this season! This coat is very nicely sewn tougher, No weird or unsightly seems or loose strands, It also has a nice sheer black lining. The coat is soft and comfortable and very flexible so it moves great layered over lots of clothing too.

I love the print and the pretty black and white. The boxy cut is also on trend and super cute and easy to wear with anything. It looks great over a dress or with trousers, jeans, leggings, or shorter skirts. It also looks really great belted too if you want to show off that lovely hour glass figure!

This coat is a great deal especially for what you pay. The buttons are also easy to do and undo when getting in and out of this coat.

I'm a size 6 and tall, and I ordered this in a large and its a perfect fit. I was especially nervous the sleeves wouldn't be long enough for my long arms (i'm 5'10) but its a perfect fit!

I adore this coat and plan on wearing it a bunch this fall as well as taking it into the colder months by layering up underneath. I love that thanks to the boxy style of this coat, it's easy to wear over lots of layers!

I received this coat at a discount in exchange for my honest review.

The logo is center except the "6" in 2016 is slightly too far to the right. The paint looks is described. It was true to size and didn't shrink when it was washed. Overall I'm pleased with the quality of this T-Shirt I just wish the 6 wasn't so far off. (Compare my photo to the original ad)

PROS:
Soft material
Fits as expected
Preshrunk

CONS:
6 is too far to the right compared to other numbers and letters

Cotton softness: *5*
Size Accuracy: *5*
Paint Quality: *4*
Comfort: *5*
Value: *5*

product_title: Coffee Lover Gift - Simple & Unique 925 Sterling Silver Coffee Ring Jewelry for Women
review_headline: Great preteen ring to give as a first jewerly gift. I also think if you have that person who loves coffee or tea.
review_body:
Ok this is a sterling silver with plating of rhodium. I have to jump on here real quick and give you my impressions of this product. I got it out of packaged in plastic. The box it comes in is cardboard. To me it could of been a little nicer of a box. I just reminds me of a discount store well known that sells jewelry. Now you can always find something else to present this in if it is a gift. I personally have been a lover of teas and coffees since my young teen years. I feel this fits my personality to the T. You will notice it is not a high setting ring. It sits very low to the hand. When you put this on there is a gap between the cup and steam. If you have to get a different size you could lightly and I mean lightly adjust it there. I wouldn't adjust it unless last resort. I love it is good weight with out weighing out your hand. Many ways this could be worn on a index to middle finger. If you are wearing on one of those fingers maybe wear it higher on the knuckle. I will wear mine when doing photos of beauty and nail products. I feel now this can be a signature piece. I am getting used to the open but it is not bad. I would warn to take it off before you put on hose or anything thin that could tear. If it got a hold of something thin it could hook on and tear it. This would be a good starter piece of someone wearing jewelry for the first time. Maybe a preteen and you could tell them it is hot chocolate steaming. Below will be pictures of how I got it and on myself.
As an active blogger I received this item for little or no cost. all opinions are 100% my own.

product_title: Coffee Lover Gift - Simple & Unique 925 Sterling Silver Coffee Ring Jewelry for Women
review_headline: Beautiful Ring for Coffee Lovers Everywhere!
review_body:
I'm a huge coffee addict and love the stuff any way I can get it. Daniel Doughty's sterling silver coffee cup ring is a beautiful way for me to show off my obsession!

My fingers will react to cheap metal, so I try to watch what I'm wearing. This beautiful ring is made of 925 sterling silver and hasn't caused my skin to react at all. The silver finish is very bright and the sterling silver is strong enough to resist bending or warping through the day. The thin band takes up very little space on my finger and is comfortable enough to wear all day!

Of course I purchased this ring for its design moreso than its function. The tiny coffee cup and steam lines resemble the iconic image for coffee that every brew junkie is familiar with. The cup and detailed lines are separated completely and there's a break in the ring in between them. The cup is wider than the band of the ring but not so much that it becomes a hassle.

Daniel Doughty's coffee ring is a gorgeous way to show my love for coffee! I did receive this ring at a discount but price doesn't change how great it looks, nor does it effect my review.

product_title: Coffee Lover Gift - Simple & Unique 925 Sterling Silver Coffee Ring Jewelry for Women
review_body: This is an adorable little ring to let everyone know how much you love your coffee!  Because of the separation between the mug and the steam, it will give enough for me to wear it on any of my fingers, not just the ring finger I ordered it in the size of. That's cool.  It is sturdy and very well made and of a higher quality than rings I've purchased at a department store in the past.  The steam part does stick out a little and it might snag on things, so I'm saving this pretty ring for date night or going out to the coffee shop with my mom friends.  It's just too nice to wear on laundry day!!  It is dainty, the cup not much wider than my finger.  It's a sweet little ring that shows that you have a quirky side and appreciate a cup of tea or a mug of coffee.  I'd definitely buy it for any barista or aspiring novelist or grad student.  I did receive a discount in exchange for this honest, unbiased review.  I would certainly buy this again for a friend.  I think it is very pretty.  : )

product_title: Coffee Lover Gift - Simple & Unique 925 Sterling Silver Coffee Ring Jewelry for Women
review_headline: GREAT ring for yourself or the PERFECT gift for a coffee (or tea) lover.
review_body:
I LOVE this ring! Well, I love coffee, so it just follows. But also, it's well made, has a classy look, and is made of sterling silver. There's no downside here.

First, it's adorable. Who wouldn't love this little homage to my favorite morning beverage? And, yes, it's a coffee ring, but I bet if you know someone who loves a nice cup of hot tea, she'd like this, too.

The ring functions a little like an adjustable ring, since it's open on the one side. I was a little hesitant about what size to order - so I erred on the large size, hoping it wouldn't matter. It turned out to be a perfect decision -- the ring slips easily over my knuckles, and then I can squeeze it down to a comfortable level of snugness.

It's also, well, just very nice looking, even thought it's fun. I would be completely comfortable wearing this to a business meeting. It's a piece of casual jewelry, but so well made I think it can work with many ensembles.

The "steam" does protrude a bit. I found it catching on various things until I got used to it.

I received this item at a discount in exchange for an honest review. Any opinion expressed is mine alone.

review_body: After ordering pants from Mountain Warehouse which were a perfect fit and excellent quality, I was confident ordering a few other products from them. I emailed them that night and the next morning I received an email apologizing and assuring me the correct items were being sent immediately and they would reimburse return shipping costs. The items arrived the next day as well as confirmation of reimbursed shipping fee.  This jacket is actually a higher quality and craftsmanship than I expected. The fit is roomy which I need for layering. Details such as velcro closures along zipper and hood are well placed, two discrete inner pockets are perfect for phone, wallet, sunglasses, keys. I love the overall quality and the color is perfect. I look forward to future purchases from Mountain Warehouse.

product_title: Dream Girl Boy's 9939 1 PC Gone Mental Costumes
review_body: I am writing to share a serious matter of importance as it relates to one of your children’s costumes.  I refer to your Gone Mental children’s costume, with the description that reads, “He has crazy thoughts in his head¡­he¡¯s GONE MENTAL. This pullover tunic features faux vinyl straightjacket straps with buckles detailing, blood splatters, and mental ward screen print. You¡¯d be crazy not to get one!” My younger daughter, once an honor student, athlete and musician before her illness presented during the onset of adolescence, has lived with schizoaffective disorder for the past six years, and was hospitalized as a child.  We’ve taken her to UCLA and Stanford, as well as our local hospitals, hoping to make sense of her devastating illness.  If you have ever spent anytime visiting a loved one in a children’s/adolescent’s mental health treatment facility, I assure you, you would understand that this costume is painfully cruel. Childhood suffering is not an appropriate inspiration for a Halloween costume.  And neither is adulthood suffering (note that you sell several other adult costumes that stigmatize and inappropriately portray the mentally ill). Vampires are not real.  Mummies come-to-life, monsters and zombies are not real.  Cartoon characters, fairy princesses and action heroes are not real.  Those types of costumes are appropriate to sell for children for Halloween.  But childhood and adolescent mental illness very real.  I doubt you would sell a Stage Four Cancer costume.  Why would you sell a costume that makes fun of a severe brain disorder? Stigma only encourages hopelessness and despair.  Please reconsider stigmatizing our daughter’s very real illness by removing “Gone Mental” and other mental illness inspired costumes from your inventory.

product_title: Mission Belt Strap
review_headline: (live video test) Coolest belt ever. Fits like a glove
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:53b2db124969d55f8671f24e58b2352]] UPDATE: This takes a learning curve to get used to. The lever that releases the pin from the teeth require that you push it in a certain direction to release it. I thought my belt was stuck, but instead of forcing it, I simply inhaled a little (to take pressure off of the belt) and that allowed me to easily push the lever and release the belt. Note that you don't want a belt that releases *too* easily, which I have experienced especially with the Bowen knife belts. (those randomly pop off, which drives me crazy)

UPDATE x2: Dang I just saw the price on this. I'm blown away by Amazon. This is a very high quality leather belt for the price. I'm a cheap skate, and I can tell you my humble minions... this would cost twice at Nordstrom.

✏️ Quick thoughts to supplement my video demonstration.

I like this belt because:
- The nylon is nice because it's somewhat \\"floppy\\" and isn't stiff like conventional leather. Granted it has the military type look (rather than the nicely dressed look that you'd associate with a leather belt), but the nylon is extremely durable and heavy duty and doesn't scratch up like leather. Awesome military belt if you're looking for one to hang a 45 off of.
- Super customization. The little notches allow me to fit it perfectly around my waste, as opposed to conventional belts that have set holes, which can be upwards of two inches apart.
- Looks awesome. Cool seeing a belt with no holes.
- Easy to put on. Stays in place and doesn't slip.
- Easy to take off, once you get the hang of it (see update above). Note: Do NOT force it! It'll just dig the \\"teeth\\" MORE into the mechanism, and you'll be stuck. Just take your time, and it'll come right off.
- True to sizing. Don't try to go \\"a size up\\" or \\"a size down\\" from you pants.

Note: I was given a sample of this product in exchange for a review and demonstration.

Hope this helps!

📍 Bottom line: would I recommend this product to one of my friends?
👍 Yes, absolutely.br />

product_title: TOP LEGGING TL Women's Comfy Versatile Warm Knitted Casual Zip-Up Hoodie Jackets in Colors
review_headline: Cute hoodie made with thermal material
review_body:
I wear lots of sweaters/sweatshirts/hoodies, because I tend to be cold a lot, and I like to layer. Plus, I live in the Northeast, so warm clothes are a must!

I chose this hoodie in purple, and I love the color. It is a beautiful vibrant purple and it is just what I wanted.

The fabric is unlike any hoodie I have had before. The thermal material is just like you would expect - that sort of thin, waffle-like material that you would find with something like thermal bottoms.

I put that the fit was somewhat small, because this has a slim, tight fit. I chose size medium, and I am 5'7" and about 125lbs, and the hoodie is not loose on me. I usually wear a size 8, which is why I chose size M. I am happy with the fit as it has a nice look to it, compared to some of my baggier, more casual hoodies. Also this is sort of long on the torso and the sleeves, which I like, as tops are often too short on me.

It does have a zipper, pockets (which even fit my iPhone 6, which is nice!) and a hood with drawstring.

This is perfect for end-of-summer mornings and evenings, as the crisp fall weather is starting to move in, and good for year round when you need some extra warmth. Overall a cute hoodie!

review_headline: I am by all means satisfied only because I bought 2 so I was able ...
review_body: I bought this item about a week ago and it came quicker than I expected. I am by all means satisfied only because I bought 2 so I was able to use one of them when they arrived. I am a 5'5 athletic built female and I wear a size medium shirt, prior to the purchase I read reviews so I strongly encourage you to do the same before buying this! Most of the reviews stated the item ran in a smaller fit but that's the purpose of using a waist trainer right? Well I received both of the Waist Trainers I purchased one for me & one for my mom (M&XL) I hate to pass up a great bargain and like I said it came QUICKER THAN I EXPECTED so I was pretty excited.. only to find that the Medium was more like an XtraSmall and the XtraLarge fit more like a Medium. The quality is very nice, and it has the right fit just as long as you have the right size. It's not so visible under clothes & there are little breathing holes throughout the entire stitching so the overall quality rating I would give it a 3.7.. I wasn't so found with the fact it's not true to size and it doesn't look like the item in the picture. And if you're wondering I kept the XL because it fits perfect & I gave the Medium to my roommate who weighs like 110lbs and she loves it. " Moral of the story " : BUY IT!! BUT MAKE SURE YOU GET IT ATLEAST ONE SIZE BIGGER THAN YOUR SHIRT SIZE (maybe 2 sizes if you want it to be comfortable) OR ELSE YOU ARE GOING TO BE UPSET WHEN IT COMES IN THE MAIL :) by the way that's the Medium compared to my MacBook in the photo attachment.. it was really small.

product_title: Bepei Women's Long Sleeves One Button Open Front Wraps Soft Cardigan Sweater
review_headline: Awesome piece to add to any wardrobe
review_body:
I was so excited when I pulled this cardigan out. with all the awesome color choices I had a hard time deciding which one I wanted but I decided on the green, it caught my eye immediately. It's a beautiful dark green color and the material is soft but not overly soft. I LOVE the asymmetric hem because it gives it character and makes it a new favorite in my closet. It's wears beautifully because of that hem too. It's not snug on part of the body.
I got an XL to wear over clothes and I think it will do perfectly. The body would be fine no matter what I'm wearing but the sleeves my be a problem with a thicker sweater or sweatshirt. So if you wear really thick clothes you may want to get a bigger. This would be an amazing accessory to turn any summer dress into an appropriate fall/winter outfit.
It's on the light side so it can be worn as a permanent wardrobe piece for the day or a light jacket that easily slips on and off when entering buildings. There is only one button at the top close to the neck. The button itself is super cute.
I received this product complimentary in exchange for my honest opinion but the opinion expressed is all my own.

product_title: Bepei Women's Long Sleeves One Button Open Front Wraps Soft Cardigan Sweater
review_headline: Love this unique style - soft fabric is very comfortable, fits perfectly, and looks great too!
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:a4649bab0c2811ea32924937a23a3615]]When I saw this Bepei one button cardigan I was really excited to give it a try, because it's totally different from anything else in my closet. Now that I've had it for a while, I am so impressed with the design and quality. The one button style is almost like a cross between a cardigan sweater, a wrap, and a poncho. If worn open, it just feels and looks like a comfortable, flowy sweater. When the oversized button is fastened, it gets more of the poncho type look. I love the asymmetric way that it diagonally goes across my body when fastened, while still keeping my arms and torso covered so they stay warm. The open design at the bottom creates nice movement as I walk around. The fabric is extremely soft and feels great against my skin. I chose the grey color which has a nice bit of heather color variation to it - I like that it is neutral enough to go with anything in my wardrobe while being a bit different from the standard black. The style is versatile enough that I can wear it to work or just around running errands, but also can dress it up over a fancier outfit and still look great. I know that I will be wearing this Bepei sweater a lot over the fall and winter - it's perfect for walking outside on a chilly evening! Itypically wear a size 8 or 10 and ordered the size Large based on the measurements provide in the item description - the sweater fits me very comfortably.

I'm very glad that I was able to order this as a free promotional sample in order to evaluate and provide my honest review.

product_title: Bepei Women's Long Sleeves One Button Open Front Wraps Soft Cardigan Sweater
review_headline: A perfect, fall piece of clothing to complement all your outfits!
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:5d7f2d6ab6d3b76c0e82084b2b4b7d8f]]This review is for the Bepei® Women One Button Wrap-Style Cardigan Black.

This cardigan is well made! It is designed with a thick, soft fabric and is ultra-soft against my skin! This is the perfect, quintessential fall piece that will complement all your outfits and works great over all tops and dresses!

The cardigan looks great buttoned or unbuttoned. I usually just throw it on over whatever I am wearing when I go out because it does a great job of keeping the chill off my skin and I am nice and warm. This is also great because you can take it off, throw it into your bag, and it doesn't wrinkle - so pull it out later and wear it again!

If you go traveling, and don't want to carry a lot of bulky warm jackets or sweaters - throw this into your suitcase! This is great for going out at night or just walking around shopping during the daytime! It is very versatile. I got the black color but I am seriously thinking about getting a few more colors to complement other outfits!

The seams are flawless and well stitched. The button is brown wood and looks good when open or closed. The length is also perfect! I am 5'8 and it doesn't sit up too high. I also got the XXL because I am a size 16 however, next time I think I will get the XL as this one is a little big. product_title: Ska Studio Shaper Shorts Levantacola with Buttlifter and Thigh Slimmer (127FA)
review_headline: Having sciatica I suffer from a lot of pain pretty much on a daily basis where I really cannot ...
review_body:
Having sciatica I suffer from a lot of pain pretty much on a daily basis where I really cannot do any of the things I love to do daily. Wearing really well made shaper shorts helps the pain tremendously and makes it easier to do things I enjoy like house cleaning, gardening, cooking, painting in my studio, building furniture, laying tile, etc., I have been wearing these Ska Studio Shaper Shorts Levantacola with Buttlifter and Thigh Slimmer for two days now after I hand washed them and hung them to dry. I cannot tell you how they have helped decrease my pain and how extremely comfortable they are. I am truly truly amazed!! They are a firm compression yet not an uncomfortable compression like many other brands that I own. I really have to say Ska Studio Shaper Shorts is the most comfortable compression out of all my shape wear, and I have a ton of it due to my sciatica.

I love the way they are made with cotton on the inside making it very soft to your skin and you will not sweat in these shaper shorts like many other brands. They are surged on all seams with no lose threads. Very very professional.

They look fabulous under my jeans, not bulky at all. The butt is a great lifter due to how it is made. It really does make your butt look very nice. I have never worn shape wear that has the butt cut out like this but I have to say I like t a lot. It is not uncomfortable in any way.

The waste and thigh has a silicone like material that keeps the shaper in place. I had no issues with the waste rolling down or the thighs rolling up. I really love these and they have become my favorite shaper’s that I own.

I am 5’2 118lbs and I ordered the small and it fit me perfectly. I normally wear an extra small so I did size up one size as the ad states to do and I believe that sizing up one size was smart as I think an extra small would have been very uncomfortable and way to tight. The thing with shaper wear is to not cut off your circulation and to not have them so tight that they are putting pressure on your internal organs as this can cause health risks. So, make sure you order a size up and if you do not want such a firm compression order two sizes up as the material these are made out of will still give you outstanding compression two sizes up. I am positive I could wear a medium and be just fine.

I received these Ska Studio Shaper Shorts Levantacola with Buttlifter and Thigh Slimmer By Ska Studio in exchange for my honest and unbiased review and opinion. I would recommend this shaper shorts for many reasons. They are very professionally made, cotton lined, added bonus of lifting your butt, and extremely comfortable. Highly recommended. 5++ If my review was helpful to you please rate it. Thank you :)

review_body: I have been wanting a moto jacket for awhile since they are popular on Stitch Fix. This one is well made and lined. The colors and pattern are nice. It fits a tad smaller than expected. product_title: Lightweight Faux Fur Sherpa Leather Fleece Vest Jackets with EttelLut Hairband
review_body:
This jacket is really cute and very warm. It is "quilted" on the outside and lined on the inside. The quality and material are both "high end", well made with very durable material and stitching. I do wish that it had some sort of collar, it just looks a little funny when zipped up but not that big of a deal. The sizing is a little odd. It is shorter than a normal jacket (most Moto jackets are) which wouldn't be a huge deal if the band at the bottom wasn't so tight. I wear a size L/XL & size 16 so I ordered an XL jacket. The jacket fits a little loose in all areas except the bottom band (fits more like a Medium). Since I will be wearing it zipped up I just stretched the band out and now it fits properly and proportionate.

** I received this product at a discounted price for my honest, unbiased review. **

review_body: I purchased the Cropped French Terry Doubl Breasted Jacket. Really cute with the double buttons and the collar stays perfectly flat. I like how the lining is slightly frayed. It adds to the appearance of it. It ran true to size for me. It is more cropped than it appears in the picture though. The jacket is made of mostly cotton so it did shrink a little bit after washing and drying. The jacket is textured too and I love that about it. All of the products from this seller are of much higher quality than I expected. They all also look better in person. I received this product at a discount in exchange for my review. The black cardigan can be dressed up or down.  It has real pockets too. The material is thick and not cheap. The sleeves are 3/4 length but overall I expect it to add enough warmth in the coming months.  The open front zipper waist blazer jacket fits perfectly. The colors are great for fall. It is fuzzy and warm. I wanted this mostly because I thought the zipper waist was a really unique feature. It looks really interesting in person. The zipper also allows it to become a crop jacket at times too. It is lined on the inside. I would have liked for the jacket to have pockets, though I suppose I will be fine without them. I received this product at a discount in exchange for my review.

product_title: Lightweight Faux Fur Sherpa Leather Fleece Vest Jackets with EttelLut Hairband
review_headline: Very CUTE but runs a little Small
review_body:
I recently purchased this cute light blazer jacket at a discount for my honest review.
I looked at the measurements and decided to go with an XL. Normally I wear a Large in most of my tops, but jackets seems to always run tighter on me. I am a broader girl in the shoulders and bust.
The black is a true black color. The jacket is like a sweatshirt material so it moves easily and will have a little warmth to it. The sleeves are 3/4 length and fit nicely. It does fit in my shoulders pretty well but even the XL I bought is a little too small. This is why I am giving it 4 stars instead of 5. I feel it isn't quite true to size but runs a little small. I wish it came in and closed more in front. I feel like it needs more material around the back to get it to close. This would be much better on a smaller busted women however I am a size 38C and not really much bigger than normal. There is NO clasp in the front to secure it shut. I couldn't quite tell in the picture if it closed or not. It does not. The front two pockets are cute and they are functional. There is a gather in the sleeves which adds character and I think is very cute. I would also say this is more of a CROP length on me. I am 5'7 and it comes right at my true waist. I think this jacket would look perfect with some cute jeans/leggings, a white tank and a statement necklace.
I live in AZ and our winters do NOT get cold so something like this is just perfect when running around doing errands and doctor appointments, but also cute for going out at night with the girls or a date with my hubby.

review_headline: This blazer looks and feels much more higher quality than you'd expect for the price!
review_body:
This blazer is gorgeous! It is made with a much higher quality than I expected too! It is thick and warm, and also has a little stretch to It. I do wish it was lined though and had a button to close it. It has some nice pockets on the side. and the cut looks great, hitting me at my smallest part, the waist. This makes a great layering piece over just about anything I'm wearing and ads some additional warmth and style!

I also really love the 3/4 sleeve with rushing detail. It feels and looks great!

I'm size 6 and normally get a medium. I ordered this in a large and it was a perfect fit.

The blazer is super comfortable and really ads some style to whatever I'm wearing! The material is also soft as well. The jacket is sewn together nicely and I didn't notice any loose threads. It has nice stitching and looks much more higher quality then what you pay for it. I got it in black and absolutely love it! This color also go great with everything!

I highly recommend this jacket to anyone who would like a soft, somewhat stretchy blazer that looks and feels high quality but is still very inexpensive!

I was given this product at a discount in exchange for my honest review.

I like that the blazer has functional pockets (sometimes other blazers have them for decoration only). There is a ruching detail on the sleeves and two pockets in the front.  I wish the ruching detail is done twice on each sleeve because it is a little bit loose for my arms. I also wish that there is a button in the front to close the blazer. For reference, I am 5'2" and 105 lbs and ordered size small. The blazer is a bit loose on me but still fits well. I am glad I had the opportunity to get this blazer at a discounted price and write a review about it.

product_title: DesertWolf Vintage Leather Casual Hiking Backpack - Messenger Bag (Brown)
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:ad67fce3bc36c38978e26a7cae336891]] What a great backpack! When I received a sample in exchange for an honest review, I wasn't expecting anything beyond the normal backpack designs, but there are a number of nice features you don't usually find that are included in this one:

=All of the leather is either double layer or backed by a tough nylon (?that's what it looks and feels like) fabric.
=There is a hidden handle inside a zipper slot on the back
=The shoulder straps are also hidden inside the zipper slot
=As an alternative, there is a single long shoulder strap that can be used in place of the backpack shoulder straps
=Everything is lined with a tough fabric that appears to be nylon
=There are pockets galore everywhere
=I managed to load a 13\\" aluminum Macbook into the main cavity, as well as a couple of very thick books
=Brass finish on all of the hardware; combined with the shiny brown leather, this thing looks really cool
=Multiple snap shackles allow you to change carrying straps at will

This bag looks fantastic, and will certainly last for many years. I am very impressed with the quality and attention to detail, and it has become my favorite bag for carrying my computer and numerous peripherals, as well as books, supplies, cables, etc. etc. Two very happy thumbs up for this wonderful backpack!

Be sure to watch the video - you can see all the features and experience how the bag works!

product_title: DesertWolf Vintage Leather Casual Hiking Backpack - Messenger Bag (Brown)
review_headline: An affordable genuine leather bag that is roomy and well made...
review_body:
This bag is, in a word - AWESOME. I have a ton of different backpacks and bags, and this is one of the best so far.

Just by touching the leather on the outside, I could tell that it was a great quality backpack. The leather is so soft and supple and has that scent that only genuine leather has. The gold accents are a nice touch and really add to the overall look.

The bag is comfortable to carry in my opinion. Since the bag comes with adjustable straps, it is very easy for me to get a fit that is just right for me.

As far as storage goes, this bag has plenty of pockets. There are two zippered pockets on the outside, two side pockets and an inside zippered pocket as well. The main compartment is very roomy. I was able to put my 15" laptop inside of the bag, and I still had room left over for me to store some other odds and ends. I received the bag for review and love it. I started carrying it around with me last week and I have already received quite a few compliments on it. If you are looking for an affordable genuine leather bag that is roomy and well made, this is the one for you.

product_title: High Quality Leather Magentic Money Clip Wallet & Credit Card Holder w/ RFID Blocking Technology.
review_body:
This RFID money clip is made of super incredibly soft, supple leather. Usually when I buy a new leather wallet or money clip, it takes some time before it is broken in and feels comfortable in my pocket. Right out of the box this one feels at home in your hand and pocket.
The stitching and seams are well done and feel like they will last a long time without any fraying or tearing.

The money clip is unusually wide but that just means more storage. I personally only carry 6 cards, ID, a few business cards and some cash, and I've got tons of space left for more. This money clip can easily accommodate double that with ease and still remain slim and manageable. I really like the amount of pockets incorporated into the design of it as well. ID pocket, large center pocket, smaller our pocket, and 3 pocket for cards.

The look of of the money clip is simple and understated, for me that's great because I'm not into flashy accessories. Also, the fact that it is RFID secure is not advertised in the branding, which is nice. I've used those paper sleeves for my cards before but they get annoying fast. Not to mention they wear out constantly. This entire wallet is RFID secure! No more paper sleeves. Ever.

Overall, a very nicely constructed, larger sized, secure wallet that I will recommend to anyone I know. My one and only issue with this money clip is the ID pocket does not have a opening in it so you can easily push your ID out, and it fits in there so snugly that it's very difficult to access quickly.

I received this item in exchange for my impartial opinion and honest review.

product_title: High Quality Leather Magentic Money Clip Wallet & Credit Card Holder w/ RFID Blocking Technology.
review_body: Very nice wallet.  I've had a slim wallet for the past couple of years and doubt I'll ever go back to a regular wallet.  As for this one, I was able to easily get 6 credit cards, 2 paper cards and my drivers license into it and still have room for more.  The money clip/holder is the only thing I would prefer be a little different.  It hold 4 folded (one time) bills fairly securely.  I would hesitate to put any more than that in the clip portion.  Also, I agree with another reviewer that I would have preferred a metal (or leather-covered metal) clip instead of the leather flip which secures with magnets.  What I may do with this wallet is remove the clip portion altogether and just put bills into the center section of the wallet.  I usually don't carry a lot of cash anyway.  The leather seems to be high quality, and the wallet is super thin.  A solid 4 stars.  I did receive the wallet at a discount in exchange for an honest review.

product_title: High Quality Leather Magentic Money Clip Wallet & Credit Card Holder w/ RFID Blocking Technology.
review_headline: I really wanted to love it.............
review_body: OK ..  I received the clip today, I was kinda excited to get it ( for my son). Now for the nice things about this clip, it seems to be made of nice smooth yet firm leather.  It has a pocket for an ID that has a clear window . The plastic is pretty thick and I believe it would  hold up for quite a while and take the pressure of sliding an ID in and out when need be. It has 3 slots for credit/debit cards and each slot has the RFID blocking fabric, which is nice and each area of the wallet/clip has this feature ensuring security. The wallet/clip has 2 additional larger slots for other items or addition cards/cash.  Now for the part that I do not like......... the clip! This is the part that really bothers me. I expected it to have some sort of pressure metal clip covered in leather.. it doesn't.  The clip is a leather flap that is secured with a magnet. There is a magnet in the flap of leather and a magnet in the wallet and thin magnet at that. So I tried to see how much this magnet would hold SECURELY! I started out with about 15 bills............  wouldn't hold, went to 12 bills, still wouldn't hold....went to 8 it finally started to grab the other magnet, but only after I flattened the crease smooth.  I went to 10 bills and again it barely held the cash in place. So I shook the wallet and the cash fell out. Now for something that went to great lengths  to secure your identity and credit card, not much thought was given to the clip. I also would be very hesitant to put any cash in the clip anyway for fear that it would become unattached pulling it out of a pocket and all the money would drop loose to the floor. Like I said I really wanted to love it and there are many things about it I do like. It is a nice quality, well constructed and the RFID Blocking Fabric in each slot,  but I think it needs to have a much more powerful magnet or use a pressure clip covered in leather to  hold the cash more securely.  I received this item at a discount for my unbiased opinions.

review_headline: classy wallet with identity theft protection!
review_body:
If you are anything like me and worry about security when it comes to your wallet, then I believe this is the wallet for you or anyone out there! It arrives very nicely packaged and shortly after you purchase it. It has a slick, classy feel to it. Appears to be leather. Has a lot of compartments for cards and even ID card. As well as cash and section for coins. I purchased this wallet for my stepdad who's birthday is coming up and I figured he'd enjoy this as a gift. I received this wallet with a discount in exchange for my honest opinion.

product_title: Premium Quality Leather Wallet w/ RFID Blocking, Excellent Credit Card Protector - Stop Electronic Pick Pocketing and Identity Theft - Blocks Identity Theft and Credit Card Data Breaches By Blocking Rfid Scans, 100% Money Back Guarantee!
review_body:
I received this product in return for my honest review.
I wasn't quite sure how to test that the wallet was RFID blocking but I read in the reviews where someone put their work ID in it and tried to open a door which I thought was cool and sounded like a good way to test, since my school ID does work to unlock doors when it is in my current wallet. So I put my school ID in the pouch closest to the outside of the wallet and it did work, as in, it would not open the door and the scanner could not sense it. I thought that was pretty cool, and is good enough proof for me that this wallet actually does what it says it does. My boyfriend is always worried about people stealing his information, so I know he will really love this wallet! I'm sure he'll do some tests of his own as well! Aside from testing what the wallet does, it also looks and feels very nice, I love the quality. It has ample amount of space inside, which is good with the amount of cards my boyfriend has. So aside from the RFID blocking, I also think this is just a really nice good-quality and good-looking wallet.

product_title: Premium Quality Leather Wallet w/ RFID Blocking, Excellent Credit Card Protector - Stop Electronic Pick Pocketing and Identity Theft - Blocks Identity Theft and Credit Card Data Breaches By Blocking Rfid Scans, 100% Money Back Guarantee!
review_headline: This might not be a great way of testing the RFID blocking
review_body: While this wallet a bit big for me, I tested the RFID blocking and it seems to work.  I put my work badge in my wallet and tried to unlock a door and it didn't read.  This might not be a great way of testing the RFID blocking, but I felt good enough about it to confirm that it has some sort of RFID blocking.  Anyways, like I mentioned before, the wallet is a little big for me, but my dad, who just so happen to be in need of a new wallet, seems to love it.  After I told him about it blocking RFID, he was very impressed (he had heard about people stealing credit cards via RFID readers on the news) so I am very happy that he now has some peace of mind over that.  He loves how there are so many card pockets, and because he's happy with the wallet, I am very happy with the wallet. The price is nice (although I must disclose that I got this wallet for a reduced price in exchange for my unbiased review), and the leather (I'm not sure if it's genuine leather or not) is soft and the wallet itself feels sturdy. If you want a good (or at least decent) RFID blocking wallet and want to have lots of space (I mean lots of space) for cards/pictures, etc, I definitely recommend this wallet.

I received this product to share my honest thoughts and opinions about it.

product_title: AW Fashion's Whiskey Tango Foxtrot-Military WTF Humor Premium Men's T-Shirt (White)
review_body:
If you don't want to wear a shirt with the expansion of WTF on it, this is the next best thing. It will certainly turn heads. It is a great way to meet strangers as somebody will certainly say something to you about the shirt. Is that a bad thing? Just tell them you got it from Amazon. With an eight year old, it was interesting explaining the shirt to him since there is nothing explicitly on the shirt. I suspect he thinks I didn't tell him everything.

I like the multiple colors available for the shirt, though I only got one, the white one. I'm also fond of the fact that the shirt is 100% cotton. The shirt is very comfortable and so far has done well with the dryer, not affecting the printing at all. Collar not too tight with plenty of room to breathe.

Might have to pick up some of these for Christmas.

Received product at a promotional price with promise of an honest, unbiased review.
