product_title: Comila Women 1950s Vintage Retro Capshoulder Party Swing Dress
review_body:
PROS:
* Looks very nice
* Stretchy fabric
* Knee length even for a really tall person.
* Seams and details are clean and straight.

CONS:
* Waist seam is 3" above belly-button on a tall person
* Arm holes are too small, and cut in at the front of the armpit
* Described sizing is a little snug.

I got one of these from the manufacturer in exchange for a review.

This is REALLY nice, but the sizing is a little off. The size variance listed is probably correct, but when you're right on the edge of sizes, and you get one on the small size of variance, it's too snug around the arms. if you get the next size up, and it's on the upper size of manufacturing variance, then it would be baggy.

It's also not made for tall women. My wife is 5'11" and the waist on this is pretty high. Maybe it's just the style, so I won't ding for that. Also, it comes down to her knees, which is impressive, even if not the intent.

If you have a shorter torso, or are under 5'8", then this is probably pretty good for you.

The 1 star ding is because of the arm holes. My wife is not a waif, but she's fairly thin, and the arm holes on the dress cut in uncomfortably in the front. It's not too tight to zip, but it does call into the stretchiness of the fabric a bit.

We'll see if the Medium has a little more arm room.

product_title: Tinacrochetstudio Handmade Crochet Boot Cuffs Wide Toppers Women Leg Warmers
review_body:
These Leg Warmers are absolutely needed for style and to keep cozy warm on those winter days! I got this pair in gray, and I was stoked to finally get them in the mail! To my surprise, they were not long warmers, but short boot topper cuffs, which is such a fantastic idea to add style, without all that extra filling in your boots!
These are homemade by a family, and the work is beyond perfect. I literally had to double check for flaws and found zero! The stitching and loops are perfect sized all around, and they are even. The toppers are about 6 inches, so they fit nice and snug right under your boot tops!
The warmers are unbelievable soft, unlike course thread, and really look expensive! I love them!
**I received this product to review in exchange for my 100% honest opinion.

product_title: Tinacrochetstudio Handmade Crochet Boot Cuffs Wide Toppers Women Leg Warmers
review_headline: These are boot toppers, it means short cuffs
review_body:
These leg warmers are made by hand. The workmanship on these leg warmers is excellent. The stitches are very neat and all of them are the same size which is a sign of that they were made by an experienced craft person.

The stock photos made me think that these leg warmers would be tall, almost to the knee. However, these leg warmers are very short. Their height (unstreched) is 6 inches. This is why they are called boot toppers - I did not know what that really meant originally. So they just decorative for the most part.

I got size Large. The width of the wide side 5.5" and the calf 4.5". These measurements are taken when the leg warmer is unstreched and they stretch quite a bit, so they should fit a very developed calf. 17"-18" circumference will work.

These leg warmers are provided at special discount for review by Tinacrochetstudio as part of the new product introduction to help buyers know what to expect.

Ali Julia review

product_title: Comila Women 1950s Vintage Retro Capshoulder Party Swing Dress
review_body:
Ok so I really love this dress! I was so excited when I received it. I wear a lot of fall colors and they are hard to find unless it is fall. I found that they had a wide selection of colors to choose from. I pulled dress from box and was surprised. It is a heavier material but not an uncomfortable weight. I immediately tried it on. All the seams were sewed nicely and hugged in all the right places. I always have to order based on my bust size and hope cloths fit, or take them in at the waist as needed. There was no need. This fit perfectly. Has a nice twirling skirt to it that makes you want to dance.

Pros:
Nice color selection.
More modest bust line.
5'6 comes just below my knee.
Heavier material which helps with how this dress lays.
Light stretch, makes for beautiful fit.
Cons:
Mine didn't come with washing instructions.
Slight color transfer in wash.

I did not contact them about washing instructions. I went ahead and washed based on material. I washed on cold normal cycle, I tumble dried on low till almost dry then I hung it up so the wrinkles would stretch out. No shrinkage issues. However I did get the dark red and it did bleed slightly, so be aware. This was offered in exchange for an honest review.

A Heather Stanhouse Review

product_title: Tinacrochetstudio Reversible Leg Warmers Handmade Crochet Boot Cuffs with Buttons
review_headline: I love these boot cuff warmers
review_body:
I love these boot cuff warmers! This comes with a set of 2 toppers, that are about 8" long, that you wear on the top of your leg under your knee, and boots over them. The best part is, they are just toppers, which don't stuff your boots full of socks and filling like other warmers do!
This is a two-toned, which you can wear either way, brown or beige! They come with stylish wooden buttons that can be slipped into the crocheted holes of the warmers. The warmers themselves are so smooth, and from the highest quality of thread!
I cannot fathom that these were handmade by a family, as they are literally without flaws! I am so ecstatic to wear these under my long brown boots here in the fall, paired with leggins and an over sized sweater! I found myself wearing them last week when the temp dropped to the lower 50s!
These are absolutely gorgeous and come at a great price!
**I received this product to review in exchange for my 100% honest opinion.

product_title: Tinacrochetstudio Reversible Leg Warmers Handmade Crochet Boot Cuffs with Buttons
review_headline: Beautiful. That's what I can describe
review_body: Beautiful. That's what I can describe. Buttons are lovely. Very stylish. When I was offered a review sample, I was perplexed. It mentioned home made and I thought this must be a small business endeavor. Quality workmanship. My daughter loves these.

product_title: Tinacrochetstudio Reversible Leg Warmers Handmade Crochet Boot Cuffs with Buttons
review_headline: Works with some styles of boots better than others
review_body:
Since I have no ability or talent for either crocheting or knitting, I really appreciate being able to purchase items that are hand made. Even for me, it is easy to tell that these boot cuffs were not machine made. They open fully into rectangles of which the size small measures about 11 inches by 7 inches high. They are very loose and stretch easily. Since there are no buttonholes, one can button them as tightly as necessary but must be careful to line up the ends evenly.

I am 5’ 4” tall and find that the long, reversible style of these cuffs makes them better suited for wearing with my shorter boots. I tried them on with several pairs of higher boots and they were problematic in that either the boot is covered by wearing them out, showing both sides, or as designed, half of the cuff must be stuffed into the boots. With soft leather boots, the added bulk and outline of the buttons inside the boots can mar the smooth look and also be uncomfortable. Also, unless one has long legs, the cuff can get bunched up to the knee.

On short boots, I didn’t have the problem of them bunching at the knees but still did not like having the buttons and excess bulk inside any of my boots. I have attached pictures that I hope may give a better perspective on the problems that I had trying to optimally place the cuffs. They do work well for me, though, as decorative lower leg warmers on my short books.

Disclosure: A complimentary product was sent to me for trial and evaluation. I have no connection to the seller or the manufacturer and my review is based solely on my perception of the merits of the product.

review_body: These socks are better than advertised.  I generally prefer merino wool even on my running socks but a friend told me to try these and I must admit they are great.  Great padding throughout the sole but thin on top so my feet don't sweat.  I didn't even realize how much the padding could make a difference but it was very noticeable after I finished up a 10 mile run yesterday.  They are great no show black running socks and even though they are low cut my shoes didn't rub at all.  My wife tried on my mediums and they fit her just fine (Women's 8.5) and she has already ordered another pair so we don't have to fight about who gets to wear them on our long runs. product_title: Sawtooth Murph Max Performance Black Running Socks
review_body:
I got these socks for my black nikes. I used these socks during my visit to the grocery store and other daily errands. There were some things I love about the socks and some things I didn't really like as listed below:

Pros
-Has a grip-able wedge in the back you can grab for easy take off
-is very visually appealing
-grips around the ankles

Cons
-Both socks says "Sawtooh L" at first I thought one would say "L" and one would say "R" representing which foot but they both say "L"
-after 1st wear they became kinda worn
-if the grips around the ankle gives out then the sock doesn't stay up correct thus you have to keep pulling the wedge

Overall:
I would recommend these socks to family and friends as a secondary accessory to a pair of shoes. I would see someone that has had ankles wearing these or someone that needs a pair of grab in go socks(the wedge is a lot more useful then you think).

product_title: Sawtooth Murph Max Performance Black Running Socks
review_headline: Great for High Performance and Recreational Needs.
review_body: These socks are amazing! I can be a princess and the pea when it comes to running socks. My feet hurt when my socks are too thin, and since I'm between sizes, my toes feel smushed if they're too thick. Sawtooth Murphs are just right. They hug your foot just enough to feel the extra support and compression there, but not so much that you feel constricted. The height is also perfect. The lip in the back doesn't fall below the heel of your running shoe and rub like some others have done in the past. Since purchasing, I've worn them on several middle distance runs, a recreational hike, and a 12 hr day of work (I have a job where I'm on my feet all day). They've passed the test in all of these areas. As a military veteran, marathoner, and outdoors enthusiast, I would wear these for any of those activities. The percentage they give back to Wounded Warrior Foundation is more than any other company I've seen so far and clinches them as my new go to brand. I highly recommend them for anyone, since they seem to fit every need. Oh and I wear between a 9 and a 9.5 in women's and the men's 7.5-10 fit great.

product_title: Vogue of Eden Women White Cat Fish Print Batwing Short Sleeves Tee
review_body:
This is an adorable tee with a kitty smooching a little fishy on the front. Normally when I see "one size fits all" I know that it usually means one size fits all small people. Not so with this top. It actually fits me which was a really nice surprise. I couldn't find any kind of a tag that would tell me what the fabric is made out of, and the description has conflicting information. First it says that it is 100% cotton, but then says it is 80% cotton and 20% fabric, LOL, whatever that means. I do know that I love the way that it feels. It is very soft and almost feels silky. I like it a lot.

The neckline is a bit wide, and I have very small shoulders so it does tent to slide off a shoulder now and then, which doesn't really bother me. It's for casual wear. The fabric is quite thin and sheer, so I would recommend you wear a nice white camisole underneath it. I'm happy with it.
Sample provided in exchange for an honest review.

product_title: Vogue of Eden Women White Batwing Short Sleeve Wishing Tree Print T-Shirt
review_body:
Boxy is in!
I love this Wishing Tree T-Shirt top! It's perfect to pair with a pair of skinny jeans, leggings, or in my case today a pair of shorts.
Exhibit A: the cut. As you can see the cut of this shirt is perfectly boxy. Allowing for movement, air flow, comfort and style. The neck line is a wide cut scoop neck which reveals your lovely collar bones without showing off any cleavage. The bottom hemlines of the shirt is very flattering "U-shaped so the sides are cut slightly higher than the front and the back.
Exhibit B: the fit. Because the material is so soft, all of the excess material falls in a very flattering way. It both hides and reveals shape. Lovely.
Exhibit C: the fabric. The blend of cotton and polyester makes this top move with easy, and breath well. It's light weight, and slightly semi sheer. Definitely have to wear a nude bra with this.
Exhibit D: how it measures up. This shirt is 27" from the shoulder to the lowest point on the hem line, and it measures 25" across at the bust line (or 50" around). The sleeves have a 16" opening. And the neckline is cut at 10 1/2" across.
I love the ease of this top. I love how comfortable it is, and the design is adorable also. It's a fun top to hang out in...especially on a hot day. (Which it is right now.)
My opinion after reviewing all of the exhibits listed above, is that I absolutely recommend this adorable top. I think it would be a nice addition to any closet.
I have received a free or greatly discounted product for the purpose of this review. The opinions are 100% mine. I have not been influenced in any way.

product_title: Neon Nightlife Men's Light Up V for Vendetta, Guy Fawkes Mask, One Size
review_headline: Vendetta Mask is stunning and makes me feel like a celebrity
review_body:
My friend and I bought these masks. I bought the Guy Fawkes mask in aqua and he bought the Saw Movie mask in red. We went to a huge masquerade party. Let me tell you, this product is an awesome conversation starter. We were approached by tons of people all night long complementing us. I think we had the best masks out of about 200 people there. Most people who approached us wanted to take a photo. It's a really weird feeling to have tons of strangers approach you to take a photo with you. We felt like celebrities for the night.

The mask is made of plastic and has a decent finish with a bit of shine. There is a wire leading to the battery pack comes from the side of the mask. I was able to run the wire above my ear then under my shirt. I put the battery pack in my pants pocket. The entire wire and battery pack was hidden except for the 6 inch area leading from my ear to the top of my shirt. My friend had long hair and was able to completely hide the wire with his hair when he wore it.

The battery pack was easily stored in my pants pocket. It makes a slight whining sound when on. When I turned it on at home in silence, I thought I was going to have to listen to it all night. But luckily once I put it in my jeans pocket I could barely hear it. Add the various sounds of a public location and the sound is completely unnoticeable.

Longevity is great. It lasted hours with no loss in brightness on a single set of batteries.

Overall, I would totally recommend this to anyone who likes attention and wants to get noticed!

review_body: I just received my mask today, looks and works great. Fits perfect, 3 different light modes, and great design to have battery pack be put in pocket or clipped to belt. Will be using this for a masquerade party in a couple of weeks and definitely will be the talk of the party when the lights go down.

This hat is truly awesome! Earlier this summer we went to Disney and the kids really enjoyed the ride, 'Pirates of the Caribbean'. They all wanted to be Captain Jack, but Disney being Disney, the souvenir hats were just too expensive, so we didn't get one.

I was absolutely thrilled to happen upon this hat! When it arrived, I was totally impressed as this is a great quality felt hat. The hat is sturdy, not flimsy or toy-like in any way. The hat was a real hit with the kids, they were all taking turns being pirates looting the ships that sailed by their imaginations!

This Kangaroo Deluxe Black Pirate Tricorn Hat w/ Snap Closures looks so authentic that DH is planning to use it as part of his Halloween costume!

This hat was a good fit for all of us and I see it providing hours of more fun! I definitely recommend it - so do the kids!!

product_title: Kangaroo Deluxe Tricorn Felt Pirate Hat Adult
review_body:
Every year, my children's school has a character fair. Each child is given a historical figure that they have to write a speech about that details that figure's life. The children stand throughout the library and say their speeches over and over again to anyone that comes. It's a huge ordeal and one that parents struggle with. We are responsible for the costumes that they have to wear. Coming up with a costume for revolutionary historical figures can be daunting sometimes. The one part of the costume that I could not make myself was the hat. I needed something that would last. Each of my children has to do these fairs every year and each one needs to wear the hat. Quality was what I needed.

After placing my order, this hat arrived two days later surrounded by a plastic wrapping. The hat is made of a thicker material with felt around the outside. The three sides to it have snaps that clip the brim to the top. I did not feel any movement in the snaps or their placement on the hat itself. Also, I was able to snap and unsnap very well too. Some costume hats are very flimsy, but not this one. It is a very sturdy and solid piece. This hat is advertised as a pirate's hat and works very well for that as well, but it works equally as well for a revolutionary historical figures hat as well.

Overall, I am very pleased with this. The durability of it means that my children will be able to use this for years to come. I did receive this product at a discounted rate for my honest and unbiased opinion, but that does not discredit the amazing results that I received.

product_title: Kangaroo's Deluxe Black Pirate Vinyl Boot Covers / Boot Tops
review_headline: I felt I should be scallywaggin', and swosh-buckelin' across the house with these pirate boot leg sleeves on.
review_body: I felt I should be scallywaggin', and swosh-buckelin' across the house with these pirate boot leg sleeves on. I put them on easily, and liked that there were 2 stretchy straps on the bottom that prevented the sleeve to move out of place.  I thought from afar that they did look like real pirate boots, and not just sleeves.  I didn't even feel the straps on the bottom of my feet when I put my regular black leather shoes on.  I think these boot sleeves are a playful, frugal way that helped transform my already owned shoes into Pirate looking boots.  I did think the Straps, Buckles, and Buttons matched the look well for a Pirate Themed Outfit.  I received product for free for my opinion.

product_title: Kangaroo Deluxe Stove Pipe Abraham (Abe) Lincoln Hat
review_headline: Quality nicely made hat and worth the price.
review_body:
I received this hat complimentary to test and review and I have to say I was impressed with the quality of the piece. It is a heavy felt like material with a satin ribbon hat band which is a nice detail. It definitely will last more than one party or occasion. It is sized to easily fit a man, a little large but not unwearable for a woman or grown child.

Unfortunately for me instead of going into my costume closet.................my granddaughter saw it and had to have it! The photo is her wearing it so I guess she is going to be "Slash"? for Halloween this year. Our friend put it on and he has a beard and we laughed because he really looked like Abe Lincoln but he wouldn't let me take a photo of him for my review.

In my opinion the quality of Kangaroo Deluxe hats are worth the price based on my own experience with the product and I would not hesitate to purchase another hat from this seller. I hope my review helps you in your own purchasing decisions.

product_title: Kangaroo Deluxe Stove Pipe Abraham (Abe) Lincoln Hat
review_body:

I am always try to scoop up any costumes, hats, and accessories that I can find, so when I got the opportunity to purchase this Abraham Lincoln style hat at a reduced rate in exchange for my honest and unbiased opinion I "hat" to get it for her.

The hat is meant for an adult size head. So for my daughter she wore a beanie underneath to keep it securely on her head. The hat is light, hard, and has a felt feel to the outside. There is black ribbon that goes around the base of the hat as well. This would be perfect for an Abraham Lincoln costume or any costume where a tall top hat is needed.

review_headline: I wear a fez now. Fez's are cool.
review_body:
Got this in hopes that it would be a perfect fez for my fiance's Doctor Who cosplay costume. While the color is vibrant and the fit is great- it's a little off for my fiance's cosplaying or costume for the 11th Doctor. Despite that, this fez is fun, fits well,and cute to boot. Even if he can't wear it for his costume, it'll be fun for other things like Halloween or hat parties (are those a thing?) and even my niece, who's three (and is a DW fan) would love to play with this. It's just big enough for my fiance's head, and fit's a bit tighter on mine but I have super curly and lots of hair verses my fiance who has a very short cut. Our cat even went to try and play with the tassel so it's pleased all of us.For the time being my fiance will just have to accept this one, and if he really wants to get the "official" DW fez, I won't stop him, but this was just my chance to get him one for the interim.

I received this item free in exchange for my honest review.

product_title: GertrLogan Beethoven's Fifth Symphony Styling T-shirt, Gray
review_headline: printed incorrectly and consequently butchered by the world's great orchestras. Despite my attempts to disseminate von Schweinst
review_body: I'll never forget the musty old stacks at Sibley Library where I first came across an obscure monograph penned by one Prof. Dr. von Schweinstein of Halle. As I combed through the pages--in the original German, of course--his compelling argument sunk in: what is perhaps Beethoven's most famous work has been, almost since its inception, printed incorrectly and consequently butchered by the world's great orchestras. Despite my attempts to disseminate von Schweinstein's seminal work to the masses, my colleagues in the music world have turned a deaf ear, but now, now!--perhaps this will convince them of the error of their ways. This magnificent shirt announces to the world, "You're all wrong," and I wear it with pride as a paean to the master himself, as should any self-respecting, historically-correct musician. You should be honored to wear it too. 5 stars.

product_title: Travel Wallet Neck Stash - Money Pouch or Passport Holder with bonus RFID Sleeve
review_body:
I’ll say upfront that my wife and I received this item at essentially no cost as part of an agreement to evaluate and rate and review it. That said, it’s absolutely something I’d buy on my own.

If you were to wade through my past reviews, you’d even see that I bought a lanyard wallet in the last couple years. That one I bought mainly because it was a waterproof container, which I wanted to keep my wallet-type items dry during a trip that I figured might be wet and rainy. But I liked having a neck wallet so much, it became my day-to-day wallet even after the trip was over.

This wallet is more handy than that waterproof one I used to wear. That waterproof one was the size of a credit card… so it could only hold items that size. This one is big enough that I’m not as limited to smaller items.

I just like how handy it is as compared to a standard wallet.

For one thing, I don’t like having a bulky wallet in my pants pockets.

For another thing, even if I didn’t mind having a wallet in my pocket, I often wear gym shorts or track pants or something similarly flimsy (because it’s so hot where I live)... and those kinds of clothes don’t have good pockets.

Mostly, though, I feel like I never waste time anymore hunting for my wallet. It’s not a pocket wallet, so I never have to hunt through laundry to see if I left it in a pair of pants. If I’m in a hurry and can’t find my wallet, I just take a quick look around (I look for the bright green lanyard string I attached it to), and I find it almost instantly. So the wallet never gets “lost” anymore.

I can’t speak to how well the RFID protection works. I mean, it’s a nice function in theory, but I have no way of testing it, really.

product_title: Travel Wallet Neck Stash - Money Pouch or Passport Holder with bonus RFID Sleeve
review_headline: I suffered a massive embarrassment - never again after getting this!
review_body:
I have to admit that when I saw people wearing these in the airports I thought they looked goofy. I mean, really, who cannot keep an airline ticket and passport in a quick to find place? Uh, well, I USED to think that. No more. Not after a huge embarrassment where I basically kept a line of dozens of people still and waiting for ME to find my stuff. I just got discombobulated and could not remember where I had put my boarding pass and ID. Typically it is in my purse but I had one too many carry-ons and no purse that day and got distracted and could not find the freaking paperwork (and you know when you are rushing and embarrassed, it is hard to stay cool and THINK. Ugh.) - Anyway, I swore that day I would look into a travel neck pouch like the ones I see people wear. So when I was offered the chance to real life test this and review it, I took it.

First, I have to say that I dont wear it around my neck. I wear it cross-body so when I bend it does not dangle away from my body. It has a pretty slim profile and I am able to fit my ID, travel paperwork and car reservation receipts, travel directions and money, and few other smaller things. You get the point. But it is not bulky. I would never put my camera or a hairbrush in there. It is about 7 1/4 inches in depth and almost 6 1/2 inches across. The strap that goes around your neck or cross body is 42 inches in length - definitely long enough to be comfortable. It is not waterproof but it is water resistant, the material is nice and the zippers are strong. There are two pouches. A smaller one that money/credit cards/ hotel key would work for and the other is as large as the pouch itself. That's where I put my papers, passport, a pen (for filling out those forms on the plane) and my cell phone. I have even taken it shopping. So nice to go hands free instead of carrying my purse which gets heavier every year it seems! The entire pouch seems sturdy and resilient. It even came with an RFID pouch to stop scammers from scanning your non-chipped credit cards when they pass by you. So I admit - I was wrong. These neck pouch wallets are VERY convenient and no more embarrassment for me.

As I mentioned above, I did get this for testing and review at a promotional price. I have a great deal of respect for this item. It has made my life easier.ouch to stop scammers from scanning your non-chipped credit cards when they pass by you. So I admit - I was wrong. These neck pouch wallets are VERY convenient and no more embarrassment for me.

As I mentioned above, I did get this for testing and review at a promotional price. I have a great deal of respect for this item. It has made my life easier.

product_title: Travel Wallet Neck Stash - Money Pouch or Passport Holder with bonus RFID Sleeve
review_headline: I Am Sure That I Am Going To Use This Everytime I Travel From Now On.
review_body: I'm one of those people that no matter how hard I try, I am never ready when I get to those passport/ID checkpoints at the airport.  I think that I just panic start moving things around in my pockets by accident when I keep pulling everything out to keep checking that I everything I need.  Well, no more.  The Travel Neck Wallet will definitely be solving that problem for me.  It's the perfect organizational ID carry kit to keep things simple and problem free when traveling.  It is actually very light weight which is important because it will be hanging around my neck.  It's design is actually very simple.  It has a strap with clips on both sides that attach (or detaches should you need to) the pouch from the strap.  There are 2 separate compartments, both having zippers which both moves smoothly and easily.  The top zippered compartment has more space than the lower compartment.  I did lay this next to a pair of sunglasses so that you can get a better idea of the size.  I also like the fact that my important documents are safely attached to my neck and not so easy for pickpockets to target. The only thing that I did notice that some of the stitching was loose.  I am sure that I am going to use this every time that I travel from now on. I did receive this product at a reduced price in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Travel Wallet Neck Stash - Money Pouch or Passport Holder with bonus RFID Sleeve
review_headline: I'll be super safe while traveling
review_body: Headed overseas and this is just what I need to feel safe.  The quality is much nicer than the pictures display.  It's a nice thick material that will hold up well.  The multiple pockets make it perfect to store all the essentials.  The strap is sturdy and adjustable.  Thanks for letting me test this out with a discount to review.

product_title: ACHICGIRL Women's Gradient Rainbow Long Fringe Bikini
review_headline: This is such a cute bikini!!!
review_body:
I fell in love with this swimsuit when I first saw it. I have been looking for a fringe bikini all summer. I love the beautiful colors. Here's a few thoughts on it:

-Size: There weren't any sizes listed, so I asked for a large. I find with these cheaper products they are often sized smaller than expected. Here's my measurements for reference:
Height- 5'9 1/2"
Weight 148
Bra size 34B
Pants size: Juniors 9 or 11, women's 8, women's jeans 30
I am more of an hourglass figure than anything else. The top is a teensy bit small. Not enough that anyone would notice, but i could use another half an inch on the sides. No big deal. When I adjust the triangle area it fits everything it in well. The bottoms fit well, but I also wouldn't mind if they had another inch of material on the sides. No big deal, it still looks fine. I also have another plain black bikini bottom I can substitute if I want.
-Material: The material is on the cheaper side. It's a tiny bit thinner than some of my other swimsuits. Honestly, this is a "lay on the lounge chair" type of swimsuit for me. I'm not going to be doing any sports or anything in it. It's definitely sufficient.
-Price: The bikini is listed at $17.99 right now. If you went to Macy's and found something similar it would easily be $50+, but have a tiny better material. This is a steal for how cute it is.
-Quality; I mentioned the material, but that's about the only minor problem. All the fringes are cut at a good length. The colors are vibrant. There are no oddities when looking at it.

Overall, this is an amazing swimsuit. My husband is in love with it and thinks it's by far the best bikini I own. I'm posting a few pictures. Note that the last two pictures are similar, but in the first the swimsuit is dry, the second is after getting it wet in the shower so you can see how it hangs when it's wet.

product_title: Bigbigfuture Women's Printed Tops Chiffon Cover up Kimono Cardigan Shawl Plus Size
review_headline: I LOVE THIS KIMONO STYLE TOP, IT IS SO LIGHT AND COMFORTABLE
review_body:
I love the new trend of Kimono style tops. I used to wear them years ago and was excited to see them coming back in style. This printed kimono style top is absolutely gorgeous. The colors of red, orange, sunflower yellow, and great pops of turquoise really make it stand out. Plus all the colors allow me to be able to match it with so many other clothes. I wore it today with a pair of jeans and a turquoise cami with several 70's bangles and it gave off a great boho look. I also plan on wearing it with a sunflower yellow slip dress and heels for date night. The kimono is very light as it is made of chiffon, so even though it was 88 degrees out today I remained comfortable. I love the loose oversized cut of this kimono, it makes it really easy to wear and layer. I went over the stitching when I took it out of the package and the stitches were all nice and tight. There was no uneven stitches nor any stitching that was too tight and pulling the fabric. The hem is perfect and even as well as the sleeves. The print on the fabric is nice and crisp with great detail. I just love it, I can wear it with just about anything and it is so comfortable you can hardly tell it is on. When ordering keep in mind this is oversized, as kimonos should be, so order accordingly. The size you see me wearing in the pictures is a size large. I love the loose fit, but I could have wore a medium too.
I received this product at no cost in return for an honest and unbiased review. I received no compensation and based my review on my own experience of wearing the kimono.

My mother is an avid photographer. She does a lot of events and always scrambles around trying to find bags for all her lenses, and items to take with her. This bag was perfect. The many slots and pockets helped keep her equipment organized and easy to find. The strap was comfortable and durable. This is a high quality canvas material. product_title: DesertWolf Sturdy Vintage Retro Cowhide Leather Canvas Professional Shoulder Messenger Digital Camera Bag
review_headline: Versatile bag, more uses than a camera bag
review_body:
This camera/messenger bag was sent to me free of charge for the purpose of testing. I agreed to write an unbiased review after I formed an opinion of how suitable I felt the item was for my use.

This bag is made from distressed leather and canvas. The leather has been scuffed, it gives the bag a hip vintage feel. Don't be offended by scuff marks and rub marks. The bag isn't \\"pre-used\\", it is designed that way.

The bag itself might be a bit narrow for large DSLR cameras and lenses, but this is a judgment call on your part. I am used to my friend's large telephoto lenses and the extra large backpack that carries them and his two camera bodies so my judgement is based on that perception. Be sure to read the measurements, this is not a typical wide camera bag. My Canon G9 and my Non DSLR point and shoot fit fine, but these don't need all the lenses. There are ample pockets for small items like batteries, cables and filters.

The yellow padded inside section is easily removed leaving the bag free as a plain messenger bag. There are padded dividers that fasten in nearly size needed to protect a large or small camera or smaller lens. (Again, obviously, check measurements for height/length of your equipment just as you should for any bag you are buying. The measurements given in the specs here are accurate.)

The bag has other uses.. Book bag, purse type bag, laptop bag, etc. The inner removable yellow pocket seems to be a good way to help protect my laptop inside a suitcase. (I like double duty things so I try to find extra uses.)

product_title: DesertWolf Sturdy Vintage Retro Cowhide Leather Canvas Professional Shoulder Messenger Digital Camera Bag
review_headline: This Is Well-Made AND Flexible To Fit All Of Your Possible Needs
review_body:
Having recently come back from an excursion in the red rock country of Sedona, not only was I covered with dust but also my camera bag suffered the worse for wear. Both of us were coated with several layers of dust, most of which was owed to the ATV ride I took around the territories, and – for the record – cleaning up my existing camera bag is NOT an easy task. When I purchased it, I was far more concerned with having the extra protection needed when hauling about the several different lenses in my collection; little did I understand at that time that I’d rarely be carrying all of them with me, so I could’ve lost a bit of bulk in favor of a pack that would be easier to maintain.

That’s why this Retro Cowhide Leather Canvas Digital Camera Bag from Winkine initially caught my eye. Looking at the pictures, it was clear that the way it was designed was for the camera section to be removed from the inside pouch, and that fact alone meant that clean-up of the exterior – the same exterior that would be exposed to the elements like dust in Sedona – would be vastly easier to manage after-the-fact.

The interior camera pouch is a bright yellow canvas with the padding built inside the material. Heavy Velcro strips are sewn along the top to serve as a protective cover when your camera and lenses are sealed within. The cover pulls back revealing the pouch, and it’s definitely large enough to house your DSLR and probably two separate lenses (so long as we’re not talking the super-big telephoto variety; and the walls are equipped with moveable canvas panels so that the user may customize the space. There’s also a handy zippered pouch in the lid/cover which allows for storage of memory cards or any other small essentials you’ll need in tow.

But what’s really superb about this is that the owner can remove the camera bag from the inside and still have a useable messenger bag, one that looks exceptional and is highly functional all the same. The bag offers a huge, roomy interior – with yet another zippered pouch where you could store your most valuable possessions such as cash, credit cards and the like – while the outside still offers up two snap pockets with additional ample space for whatever you might have on your person. There’s another loose pouch on one end – the kind typically reserved for a water bottle – that caps off the design.

Highly recommended. The best thing about this bag? You get two for the price of one, as Winkine’s designed their cowhide leather canvas sack with removable pieces so that it can serve as an amply-sized messenger bag. It’s a great looking piece to complement whichever ensemble you choose.

In the interests of fairness, I’m pleased to disclose that the fine folks at Winkine provided me with sample testing product of their Retro Cowhide Leather Canvas Professional Digital Camera Bag by request for the expressed purposes of completing this review; and their contribution to me in no way, shape, or form influenced my opinion of it.bag offers a huge, roomy interior – with yet another zippered pouch where you could store your most valuable possessions such as cash, credit cards and the like – while the outside still offers up two snap pockets with additional ample space for whatever you might have on your person. product_title: DesertWolf Sturdy Vintage Retro Cowhide Leather Canvas Professional Shoulder Messenger Digital Camera Bag
review_headline: Don't Shoot the Messenger.... Bag! Roomy & Looks Great!
review_body:
Photography, like any hobby, has a plethora of accessories; in addition to being expensive, the task of lugging them with you as you travel can be tedious. Whether you are a novice in the field or a professional who is sought out for weddings or model shoots, finding a storage solution that not only protects your investment, but is also roomy and not bulky can be a challenge. Fortunately, I have found that the Winkine® Retro Cowhide Leather Canvas Professional Camera Bag, and here are my impressions of it.

Construction

The title for this product is a bit misleading insofar as the construction of the bag. The bag itself is constructed from heavy-duty canvas, while the front straps which close the flap and a piece on the arm strap are made from leather. The padded insert (the yellow object in the pictures) is made from canvas as well, with some mesh pockets that appear to be nylon. Also, the buckles that you see on the front of the bag that feed through the straps on the pockets are actually decorative; the “slot” is actually sewn onto the strap itself and has a magnet attached. The magnet then connects to another on the front of each pocket and look similar to clothing snaps. That being said the magnets are strong enough to keep the large flap closed, and short of dumping the bag upside down they will remain secured.

In terms of the actual construction, the bag is stitched very tightly with no loose threads or badly-secured pockets and/or zipper. The padded insert is also well-made and customizable; the “lid” for it is connected with a sturdy Velcro® and can be removed completely for quick access. In addition, there are two yellow dividers that connect to the inside of this compartment via Velcro®; you are able to setup the dividers to whichever width needed to accommodate your gear. Lastly, if you wish to remove the yellow compartment completely you may do so, thus converting the main bag into a large side-satchel that is large enough to fit most E-Readers, iPads, Android/Windows Tablets, and smaller laptops.

Use

The Winkine® Retro Cowhide Leather Canvas Professional Camera Bag (WRPCB for short) is very well-made and durable. This is a bag that will be able to withstand considerable abuse, and is roomy enough to store virtually every type of photography lens, flash, transfer cables, cleaning equipment, spare batteries, and so forth. In fact, the only thing that will not fit is a full-size tripod, which is generally not a good idea to store with an expensive camera anyway. Thus, in terms of capacity, the WRPCB is an excellent bag.

The WRPCB is also a great storage bag without the yellow padded storage section. Thus, if you are in need of a quick satchel for work, a weekend trip, or to tote around things for school, the Winkine® bag serves that purpose amiably. There are several small storage pockets: two on the front, one on both sides, and an inner zipper compartment. The back of the bag has a vertical strap with a loop, enabling you to feed a strap through it (think of a large belt loop). All-in-all, this bag has a lot going for it and is constructed with quality in mind. That being said, there are two aspects that prevent me from giving this bag a flawless score. They are minor points, but I do feel had they been included in the design, the WRPCB would be a perfect answer to the storage question for cameras/accessories.

1) There is no handle on the top of the bag, preventing you from carrying it any way except over your shoulder. It would be nice to pick up the bag and be able to hold it without using both hands (and arms!). That being said, since the flap on the front secures via magnets, which do have a good attraction, a heavy bag could result in the flap opening and spilling contents on the ground. While I understand the decision to leave this off, replacing the magnets with actual snaps or proper belt buckles would eliminate the flaw.

2) The flap itself is rather small, which is great when you want quick access and do not want to have to fuss with excess fabric, but also limits the “bulk” of the bag. Think of someone with a large tummy wearing a t-shirt, versus a skinnier person wearing the same size shirt. The flap on this bag is the equivalent of the t-shirt on a skinny person; while it looks great under “ideal” conditions, it does limit the amount of things that you can carry in the bag if you wish for the flap to close properly.

Final Say

This is a high-quality bag that offers ample storage for most camera and their accessories. The Winkine® Retro Cowhide Leather Canvas Professional Camera Bag is well-made, looks great, and offers a customizable storage insert to accommodate a wide variety of photography equipment. That being said, this same insert can be removed to turn this bag into a simple satchel, thus making it a chameleon for all sorts of travel and storage needs. There are some minor flaws in the design, but in the end, they are not enough for me to say that this is a bad product. Thus, whether your purchase is for yourself or a loved one, the Winkine® Retro Cowhide Leather Canvas Professional Camera Bag is a worthwhile investment that will last you a long time with proper care. Final score? 4 stars of 5.

**Disclaimer: This product was sent to me by the manufacturer at no cost to review. While I do not feel that this influenced me in any capacity, I am legally obligated to disclose this fact so that you can come to your own conclusions about the merit of this analysis.**aw.

product_title: Zoozie LA Women's Bell Bottoms Flared Yoga Stretch Pants Tie Dye High Waist
review_body: I like the Womens Pants Tie Dye Bell Bottoms High Waisted Pants By Zoozie LA. I wear a size 16 in pants and I ordered these in a large. They fit nice and are so comfortable to wear. I love the tie dye pattern and the flared leg look. They are 95% Rayon and 5% Spandex. Hand wash in cold water or dry clean. Stitching is good on the pants and there are no loose threads. I like that I can wear them for lounging around the house or dress them up with a pair of high heels or wedges. I have a lot of tops that will go perfect with these pants. I like these pants a lot and am happy I got them. I received this item at a discount  for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Zoozie LA Women's Bell Bottoms Flared Yoga Stretch Pants Tie Dye High Waist
review_body:
I was a little apprehensive getting these bell bottom pants, but they are seriously very cute!!! I am 34, 5'5" and around 135 lbs so I ordered a medium and they fit perfectly! As I was strutting around my house, one of my 12 year old daughters stopped me and started raving about how much she loved them so I changed and let her try them on. She is almost as tall as me, but WAY skinnier and they fit her perfectly as well. I promised to share them with her so she is beyond thrilled.

Since these are a little long, I prefer to wear my wedges and the pants fall just above the ground. The material is a bit thin which is great for keeping cool, but I do recommend wearing a natural colored undergarment as my pink lace showed through a bit. I did have to really look, but I would rather be safe then embarrassed later. All of the seams appear to be sewn very well and if you need to, the bottom could easily be hemmed up a little to reach your perfect length. I have worn and washed these a couple of times with a regular load of clothes (no zippers!) and have only positive experiences.

I am very pleased with the quality and comfort of the bell bottoms. I received this pair for free to test out and provide my honest feedback.

product_title: Zoozie LA Women's Bell Bottoms Flared Yoga Stretch Pants Tie Dye High Waist
review_body: These pants are so funky and so cool!!  I am usually a little more reserved with my clothing choices but when I saw these I couldn't wait to get them and try them out.  I loved the black and white pattern combination.  Since they are very elastic, they fit very well.  Sometimes I have a hard time finding pants that fit comfortably since I am more curvy so when I find a pair of stretchy pants that look this fabulous, I have to have them!  I really like a comfortable high waist pant as well because it gives great tummy control.  They hug my curves nicely.  I love the flared leg as well.  It gives these pants such a beautiful flow to them that makes them great for a night out and easy to dress up a bit.  They are a very great mix of feminine, fun and flashy!  They are eye catching for sure.  The material is thin enough that they are quite breathable and airy.  Love these with heels!  They are a bit long, so make sure to keep that in mind if you are on the petite side.  I received this product complimentary in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Zoozie LA Women's Bell Bottoms Flared Yoga Stretch Pants Tie Dye High Waist
review_headline: Very comfy, soft, elegant and true to the size
review_body:
It is a very soft and comfy high waisted bell bottoms pants. These are Tie dye pants which are available in many colors, designs and sizes. I got in large size. It fits me very well. The bell bottoms pants are stretchy and feels very comfortable. I can easily sit, bend and do everything wearing these pants.
The material of the bell bottom pants is very gentle, soft and stretchy. The color combination is wonderful. It can go with many colors of tops, shirts, blouse and even long shirts. I wear this with my cultural long shirt (kameez) and it looks so beautiful.
The fabric is high quality. This is not a cheap one which gets lint after few wash.
Also you can style it with flat, wedges, sandal or high heels.
It is true to the size. Fits perfectly.
I love wearing these bell bottom pants at home, a day out, bday party, graduation or any event. They look beautiful, elegant and stylish.
I have got so many compliments wearing these beautiful comfy pants.
I would highly recommend these Tie Dye bell bottom High waisted pants.
I am so glad I got these amazing pants on a promotional discounted rate in exchange of an unbiased opinion. However it didnt effect my thoughts about it.

product_title: VSVO Women's Boyfriend Distressed Cropped Ripped Jeans
review_headline: Length of 35" for all sizes is not the inseam length!
review_body:
The description is inaccurate or not complete. It lists the length as 35". As most jeans are sold by inseam length, I believed the inseam to be 35".
Since I usually take a 31" inseam, I figured this would be great - give me the correct amount to roll up as shown in the listing photo.
The seller measured the outside length. The length of 35" is from the waistband to the bottom of the jeans measuring on the outside.
Way too short. If you order these jeans, be aware of this fact. I ordered a 33" waist size, but the length for all sizes is 35".
Otherwise really nice jeans - ripped just the right amount and the fabric is nice and soft.
Oh, but I just remembered - the buttonhole was not opened. The sewing was intact, but they never slit the fabric so you could button them.
I could have done that if they hadn't been so short. I'm really bummed!

product_title: BTOOP Canvas Bookbag Casual School Backpack Cute Schoolbag Set 3 Pieces for Teen Girls
review_headline: Adorable Giraffe Printed Backpack Has Tons Of Room For All Back To School Needs!  Pockets & Storage Galore!
review_body:
This Backpack by BTOOP is awesome! It is very sturdy and I noticed right away that all of the stitching is even and tight. It comes in blue and pink, but the blue would be fine for a girl, too because of the adorable little giraffe print all over it. There is a zippered pouch on the back and deep, slender pockets on each side. The straps have a very comfortable and supportive neoprene like material in the lining which keeps it from cutting in on the shoulders. The straps are also adjustable and there is a large loop at the top to hang it in a locker or on a storage rack at home. The zipper pulls are large and easy to find and they and the bottom are made of tan leather.

Once you unzip it and open it up, there is a large, lined pocket to keep a tablet or other electronic device. It opens wide for deep storage of books and there are also two small pockets on the inside to hold plenty of other items. I am quite impressed with the high quality and design of this bookbag. It far exceeded my expectations and is perfect for back to school! I am so glad I was chosen to receive this as a sample, in exchange for my honest, unbiased opinion and feedback. I definitely recommend this backpack and I wish I had one like this when I was in school.

product_title: Free to Live Women's Two Toned French Terry Caftan Poncho Top Blouse Made in USA
review_headline: THIS CAFTAN/TOP BY FREE TO LIVE IS VERY COMFORTABLE AND FLATTERING
review_body:
I really like this easy to wear shirt/caftan by Free To Live. It is very similar to the tops I normally purchase at a MUCH higher price. The shirt is made from French Terrycloth and is so very soft and comfortable. I am petite and normally shirts that have lots of flowing material overwhelms my small frame, but where this shirt has seams on each side from your hips to waist it is very flattering. I like the scoop neck too. This is going to be my "go to" shirt for days out shopping, and running errands. It is easy to wear, and flattering. The shirt/caftan washes up well too, I machine washed it in cold water and let it line dry (tip-hang your shirts upside down to dry).
I purchased this product at a reduced price in return for an honest and unbiased review. I based my review on my own use and opinion of the Free To Live top.

product_title: Free to Live Women's Two Toned French Terry Caftan Poncho Top Blouse Made in USA
review_headline: This is a great shirt and I really like it
review_body: This is a great shirt and I really like it. It fits well and as expected for the size that I ordered and it is really nice. It is a soft and comfortable to wear. I love how it flows and it wears. You are still able to move your arms in the shirt with ease even with the sleeves and I like how they sit. The shirt can be used for many different occasions and it is light enough to wear in the summer but it does keep you covered and protected. I received this product to share my honest thoughts and opinions about it.

product_title: Free to Live Women's Two Toned French Terry Caftan Poncho Top Blouse Made in USA
review_headline: This is a great great slip over
review_body: This is a great great slip over. The build quality is amazing and the feel is just right. Nice and soft and very good looking and fit.

product_title: Free to Live Women's Two Toned French Terry Caftan Poncho Top Blouse Made in USA
review_body:
I'm not usually into ponchos, but this isn't your average poncho. It has stitching to make a sleeve, and sits on the waist. It feels like a sweatshirt, but lightweight. I love the contrasting colors, makes it look dressier. I wish they had added a stitch or two with the batwings, they flop around and you see the inside of the fabric. I may add my own. I'll add some pics, after its out of the wash. I was so excited I threw it right in. It is really cute on, and so soft and comfortable. I imagine this as a new favorite for me. I wear a size 8, 36c bra, and I bought the medium. It fits perfectly. It fits like a shirt, and I love it.

review_headline: Fits just right - so comfortable!  Love the flowy asymmetrical style to help mask the extra weight around my tummy!
review_body:
This tanktop from Free To Live fits me beautifully and feels great. The rayon/spandex blend is soft against my skin, has a comfortable stretch to it, and moves nicely as I go about my day. I like the wide cut to the straps so that my bra straps aren't constantly peeking out. The armholes are very comfortable, not tight like some tank tops I've tried. I like the asymmetrical flowy cut at the bottom - it adds some interesting visual contrast and also seems to be slimming, since it brings the eye away from the tummy area. It can be worn casually for a summer day out of the house or dressed up with jewelry, a skirt, and a nice scarf for a fancier look. I know that I am going to get a lot of use out of this top!

I'm very glad that I was able to order this at a promotional discount in order to evaluate and provide my honest review.

product_title: Free to Live Long Flowy Shark Bite Asymmetrical Hem Tank Top Tunic Made in USA
review_body: Super cute tank top tunic.  It has a long, flowy body with a "shark bit" bottom hem.  The sides come to points and dip down lower than the curved front and back.  So it looks like something like a shark took a bite out of it.  It's a trendy look right now and I've seen it in several stores.  The tank is made of soft jersey fabric - 95% Rayon, 5% Spandex.  The material is light weight but not see through thin.  It feels so nice against the skin.  I feel confident wearing it as it looks smooth on, hugs the curves a little bit while flattering coverage.  It's fun to wear out on a casual day running errands or dressing up for a night out.  I was able to purchase this item at a discount in exchange for my honest opinion in a review.

product_title: FUN TOES Men's Toe Socks Lightweight Breathable-Value 6 PAIRS Pack- Size 6-12
review_body: [[VIDEOID:f144768302424f9cf81edc42b4efb44]]We always love silly and interesting socks. When we got the chance to try out some Fun Toes socks, we were very excited....   The Fun Toes socks come in a range of colors- black with gray toes, blue with red toes, gray with orange toes, white with blue stripes and blue toes, and them whit with gray toes ( the ones pictured above ).....   These socks are sized to fit a men's 10-13- shoe sizes between 6 and a 12.5. I wear about a 5.5 in men's shoe size, and I could get away with wearing these Fun Toes socks..   The Fun Toes socks are made  of 70% Polyester, 25% Nylon 5% Spandex. They do leave your feet feeling cool and dry, and are very breathable.   Although these socks can be worn with any shoe, they are designed to be worn with five toe shoes. They are made to reduce friction and shorten your chances of getting blisters...   I really loved that this sock comes in a six pair set, what a bargain!! I think these are really well made socks. The material is very comfortable and breathable...   I did receive this product, free, in exchange for my honest and unbiased opinions. The statements above are my own...

review_headline: Each Toe Feels Like It Has Its Own Individual Sock!
review_body: I received this product for free in exchange for my honest review. The Fun Toes Socks for Men are very nice fitting socks. My son likes them very much. They stretch to fit and each toe feels like it's wearing its own little sock! They're also very soft and comfortable.

product_title: FUN TOES Men's Toe Socks Lightweight Breathable-Value 6 PAIRS Pack- Size 6-12
review_body:
I got these for my 11 YO daughter but since it was a 6 pack I snagged a paid as well. These socks are nostalgic for me. I remember wearing them when I was younger. I've always enjoyed the toe socks. It doesn't bother me having the fabric between my toes. I'm not a toe shoe person though so these were tested in original style shoes. These socks are lightweight, breathable, and comfortable. I like the thinner material so my feet don't sweat in tennis shoes. The ankle cutoff was the perfect height for my size 10 feet (woman's sizes). They just barely show when I wear them with my shoes.

My daughter has smaller feet but these fit her as well. They fit more loosely on her and the material stretches more to fit my feet. I believe she's a woman's size 4. (In the photos my feet are the black pants and my daughter's are the purple pants)

PROS:
Soft
Light weight
Comfortable
Nostalgic
Built in heel cutout (see pics)

CONS:
Pinky toe piece is a little long

I was shocked at how amazingly well these jeans fit - They have a tiny bit of spandex in them so that they are just a little bit stretchy, but appear as though they are a sexy type of tight fit - which usually means - cut your circulation off - can't sit for too long - button popping - tight fitting jeans...

Not these jeans!! They actually feel as good as they look and hug my curves and sparkled in all the right places, and I just can not say enough how much I recommend them!

product_title: Polare Men's Classic Genuine Leather Flip Tri-fold Wallet
review_body:
**I received this product in exchange for my honest, unbiased review.**

Upon opening the package, you can already smell the new leather scent, which I absolutely love! The wallet is 100% real genuine cowhide leather with 3 card slots, 3 ID windows, 2 hidden card pockets and 2 full length cash compartments. So this wallet has a ton of space to put your cash, ID, credit/debit cards or any other cards you may be putting, and you can also put pictures in the ID windows, which is pretty awesome since there're 3 ID windows. However, I have to say that I was not a huge fan of the middle section (Shown in the pictures) since it was not removable, so beware if you don't like that. For quality purposes, I don't think it'll last long, since I noticed that the glue in the bottom of the cash compartment was already wearing off. But you get what you pay for, and for $14.99 for this wallet, I think it's a decent price. So if you're looking for a nice, cheap, decent leather wallet, well then I think this is the wallet for you!

product_title: Polare Men's Classic Genuine Leather Flip Tri-fold Wallet
review_body:
Exactly as described and shown in ad!

Positives-
*Nice soft leather, with genuine leather smell. :-)
*3 windowed picture or ID slots. (middle swinging part is NOT removable.)
*2 full length sections for cash and or receipts/documents
*space behind leftmost cards to put other cards/receipts/lunch punch cards etc.
*no brand name markings on it

Possible negatives-
*(middle swinging part is NOT removable.) for those that might want to remove it, for any reason.
*no brand name markings,(If you want that.)
*If you want this for a gift be aware it did not come in a box or other attractive packaging. (it was wrapped in foam wrap inside a fitted/sealed plastic bag, it came well protected, but would not be the most attractive way to present as a gift.

It was time for a new wallet, so when offered this wallet at a discount in exchange for my fair and impartial review, I jumped on the opportunity, and I'm glad I did. This is a great wallet! It meets all my needs, so give it 5 stars! If I was buying as a gift, I would have to give it a 4 though, due to the packaging.

I hope you find my review helpful!!

product_title: Polare Men's Classic Genuine Leather Flip Tri-fold Wallet
review_headline: Soft, and quality leather men's wallet.
review_body:
I really like this men's leather flip tri fold wallet. My husband was in need of a new wallet, as his is falling apart. He prefers a leather wallet over nylon or other material, and something rather simple and easy to use as well.

This leather wallet came in thin but soft, foam pouch to keep the leather protected. When taking it out of the pouch it has that nice, new leather smell. The black leather is extremely soft and smooth and the fine stitching that goes all around the edges of the wallet are straight and nicely done. When opening it up on the left side are three slots for store cards, credit cards, or other cards of that size, and underneath is enough room to slide a few more cards if needed. There is a middle see through pocket that moves from right to left and is attached, that will fit my husbands work ID on one side, and his drivers license on the other side. On the right side of the wallet is another see through pocket to hold a picture of our son. This wallet doesn't have any slots for pictures other than the one, but we have a plastic insert that can be slide under the right side pocket to add more pictures if he wanted to.

My favorite part is that this wallet has two soft lined bill compartments in the back. We're going to head to Europe to visit family for the holidays, and my husband will be carrying both currency for the US and for Europe. Having a place to keep both currencies separated is a big plus for us! There is also enough room for receipts to keep in the back as we're traveling to keep track of all our purchases. Overall, we're both really happy with the look and feel of this wallet. It's functional and will work wonderful for my husbands needs!

Purchased at a reduced cost for the purpose of inspection and honest, unbiased review.

product_title: LOUISE MAELYS Sexy Chiffon Beach Cover ups Swimsuit Sarong Beach Dress Skirt
review_headline: Pretty, timeless, comfortable, and true to size
review_body:
This summer has been a bit tough for me as a mom to a newborn with all the extra chub and flab around my belly. I can't parade around in a bikini like I used to, but still want to be dressed appropriately for the beach or the pool. The beach dress is very comfortable to wear, its a black halter beach dress, its a thin swimsuit material. When it gets wet, it dries quickly just like swimsuits do when they're wet. The dress fits to the middle of my thigh, it fit me perfectly and is the perfect addition to my summer beach wear. Its black so you can layer it over any color that you'd like. I am 5'4 and I have a larger bust so this may be a bit longer on someone with a smaller chest. It fit great around my back and neck and wasn't too tight around with the back area. It is a little bit sheer, but its a cover up so I didn't expect it not to be somewhat sheer and breathable fabric.

The dress is very flattering on my and I don't consider myself skinny. I normally wear a large and the size large fit me perfect, so it is also true to size. The dress is beach dress is a nicely made, its a great quality dress with excellent stitching. I have gotten so many cheap style cover ups and this isn't one of them. The neck has a double tie on each side of the neck that gives a really pretty cinched look around the neckline. Its a beautiful beach dress and timeless. Great if you go to the beach often or love lounging by the pool. I love this beach dress compared to many of the others that I have since its so lightweight and a breathable fabric, I'm not sweating in the hot sun by the time I get into the pool.

Complimentary sample provided in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: One Piece Floral Ruched Halter Push Up Slim Tummy Control Tankini Swim Dress
review_headline: Warning to All Girls with Wide Hips!!
review_body: I'm 5'7 125-130 pounds, with measurements: Bust 34", Waist 27", Hips 36" (measured just above the butt), so it seemed like XL would be perfect, according to their sizing chart. I normally wear a S or M in shirts and a size 7 pants in junior or size 4-6 pants in women's, and I buy 34B bras. I consider myself pear-shaped.  However, I wasn't able to fit in the XL (it would not go up past my thighs!). Since this is a one piece, your hips *must* be able to squeeze through the smallest part of the bathing suit. The suit is *not* very stretchy. If you have wide hips or a big butt, this is going to be a problem. I would suggest measuring the widest part of your body and then seeing if you could squeeze into the bust measurement with a few inches added for stretch. The XL is 12 inches wide at the bust when not stretched out (picture attached) and only 15 inches across when stretched out, so I would say you have to have ~30-32 inch hips to fit into it (pictures attached). The XXXL is ~14 inches wide at the bust. Add 2 inches for stretch, and that's a 16 inch bust across, so the diameter of ones hips could be 36 inches, which is exactly what I am and I was able to fit into it.  The XXXL fit very well, although I still barely squeezed into it! :P  Other than the sizing mishap, the bathing suit is gorgeous and is amazing quality. The colors are vibrant and beautiful and it is comfortable. The bottoms are shorts not a regular bikini, as suggested by some of the photos, but I like that.  **Photos: both photos of me wearing the bathing suit are XXXL, the bathing suit on the floor without a measurement is the XXXL, the one that measures ~14 inches across is the XXXL, and the one that measures 12 inches across is the XL. Hope they help!

product_title: Women's Ultra Sheer Control Top Shaping Pantyhose Tights
review_headline: Really, really good fit and comfort
review_body:
I like these so much, I stocked up. The first pair came as a free item for offered to me for review by the manufacturer, but I was impressed enough to immediately place an order for a half dozen after I tested them. Now, I'm nervous that Amazon will stop selling them, or they will change, somehow. These stockings are nearly perfect.

They are long enough for me (and I am not only almost six feet tall, my legs are long because I'm short-waisted.) I have the usual over-50 problem of bigger hips and tummy and these fit well. They have some shaping so skirts fit smoothly over them. The knit is smooth and silky, not rough. And they don't run the second you put them on--even though these have sandal-foot style toes (no reinforcement in the toe portion.) While this means you can wear these with sandals, it also means that they are more liable to have your toe poke through eventually. I prefer reinforced toes, but no one seems to make them anymore, and these fit so well, I'm satisfied.

The mocha color is a \\"your legs are suntanned\\" look, so if you typically use tanning booth, artificial tan or if you are tanned, the mocha looks summery. I wear the lighter \\"nude\\" color for everyday wear the rest of the year and with business suits in general. The mocha is great with summer dresses for more formal occasions, if you don't want to go bare-legged.

I haven't found stockings I liked since I was living in Europe and buying Falke from Germany. Those expensive hose came in foot sizes for us bigfoot types and I still own a pair after fifteen years that haven't run yet. Since Falke are expensive and hard to find, these Bonas stockings are a good substitute. Maybe not as strong, and maybe not available in so many sizes and colors, but really, really good.

product_title: Women's Ultra Sheer Control Top Shaping Pantyhose Tights
review_headline: Very sheer, but the control top fits well and is very slimming.
review_body:
These are sheer tights, that fit well and are pretty slimming. As with any sheer tights you have to be careful with them or they can get a run. These are comfortable, fit well and the control top is nice and slimming. It's a sheer toe tight so it lasts longer if worn carefully with closed shoes.

The nude ones are so sheer that they will disappear and with black tights you can see a light black color, so they're ultra sheer and ultra sexy, especially as the control top is very shaping but does not roll down.
[Received free or discounted product to test for a candid review]

product_title: Women's Ultra Sheer Control Top Shaping Pantyhose Tights
review_headline: We all need a little glamour in our lives
review_body:
My sister is the only person I know who still wears pantyhose. She wears them occasionally when she wants to "glam it up." She's tall 5'8" but slim so she usually buys a S/M and these fit as expected.

She LOVES the quality. They are sheer, but not ravelly and the stitching in the pantie part is very well-done. They look great on. She's only worn them once, but was able to tell that they aren't inclined to snag and run.

The pantie is a bit more constricting than she likes, although she says it's not uncomfortable. It's clearly designed to "mold" your thighs, tummy and rear-end into an attractive shape and it does the job. She especially appreciates the nice vent panel in the crotch area. Some "control" pantyhose skimp on that and can become very uncomfortable after a few hours.

****I was given a free sample of this product in exchange for an honest review.**** According to my tester (who buys pantyhose regularly) these are excellent quality - both material and workmanship- and she says the price is good. It won't work miracles, but if your curves aren't exactly where you want them, it will give you a slimmer, smoother look under a slinky dress. Then when you're finished strutting your stuff, you can go home and "slip into something more comfortable."

product_title: Bonas Women’s 15 Den Ultra Sheer Toe Control Top Shaping Pantyhose Tights
review_headline: Classy, high-end pantyhose -- they look and feel great!
review_body:
These are high-quality, silky, sheer pantyhose that fit beautifully and feel very comfortable on. I was especially impressed with the lush feel of the stockings themselves - these definitely feel like high-end nylons. The control-top panty is contoured to fit (unlike the shapeless panty you find on less expensive pantyhose), yet it's comfortable and not binding. Instead, the panty smooths you, which is exactly what you want.

I'm 5' 6\\" and 150 pounds, and the M/L size fits me perfectly. In fact, there is room to spare. The pantyhose were easy to put on, didn't snag (as has happened with many other pairs I've purchased), and looked great all day.

My only complaint is the toe has no protection, meaning it's likely these won't last all that long for me. If you're wearing open-toed shoes or sandals, obviously you don't want reinforced toes in your pantyhose, but I've found that the sheer toes tend to snag too quickly. I'll see how these hold up over time.

Bottom line, these are very nice pantyhose at a very reasonable price. I highly recommend them.

[Please note: I was provided a sample of this product for review; the opinions expressed here are my own.]

product_title: Bonas Women’s 15 Den Ultra Sheer Toe Control Top Shaping Pantyhose Tights
review_headline: creates a bulge around the top
review_body:
I'm 5'4" and 145lbs. I received the M/L size for review, and they are nice, but they barely fit. The sizes are listed as:
S/M = 5'0"-5'4" and 90-140 lbs
M/L = 5'4"-5'10" and 130-180lbs
X/L = 5'7"-6" and 170-210

So, at my ht and wt I am at the very low end of the scale for the M/L. I should have probably been able to get the S/M, but I went up a size instead. Even with stretching the things tight, the crotch region doesn't actually reach my crotch; there is a gap. Also, I was hoping that the way the butt area is designed, that it would provide some lift, but it doesn't.

Lastly, my main complaint with these things is that the waist band come up very high (3 inches under my breast) and is much tighter than the area directly under the band. So, there is not enough "control" in the control top, but the waist band area is tight. This leads to the creation of bulges, particularly a slight muffin top. It isn't bad, but I don't normally have those bulges, so to have panty hose that are meant to control stomach fat actually create a bulge, it's a little annoying.

They either need to make the band looser, or the control top tighter.

I received this item as sample for review, either free or at a discount. I am keeping it for permanent personal use. These are my honest thoughts.

product_title: Anni Coco® Women's 1950s Cap Sleeve Swing Vintage Party Dresses Multi Colored
review_body:
I received this product at a discount in exchange for my honest review. All opinions are 100% my own.

I was very excited about this dress because I love the style and color (I ordered the blue w/white polka dots). Unfortunately, it didn't live up to expectations. First of all, in the description it clearly states that the fabric is 96% terylene,4% spandex. The tag on my dress says 70% cotton, 15% polyester & 15% rayon. If I'd know it was cotton I never would have purchased it because cotton wrinkles so badly. The tag also says do not wear in direct sunlight. That really confuses me because I go outside so I will be in the sun. Sometimes there is an outdoor wedding or other occasion that I would wear a dress to that requires me to be in the sun several hours. Lastly, the fit is all wrong. I ordered a medium based on the size chart, but it fits much more snugly than it should. The dress is beautiful and I really wanted to like it, but I just can't. I am returning this.

product_title: Anni Coco Women's Pleated Bodice 1950s Vintage Rockabilly Swing Dresses
review_body: This dress is beautiful, but make sure you order it a size larger than you expect (or maybe two sizes).  I am normally an XS-S and I ordered a medium.  Around my ribs it is a little too tight, as well as a strange fit behind my arms.  It sort of pushes your shoulders forward, but has a bump up at the base of the neck. You will not be able to lift your arms up over your head while wearing it so I hope your hair is perfect. After washing it a few times it does start to fuzz up easier, but nothing a lint roller can't handle.  I will continue to wear this dress as I think it is adorable, but I wear a sweater over it so that I don't have to zip it all the way up.  I received this at a discount for my honest review.

product_title: Anni Coco Women's Pleated Bodice 1950s Vintage Rockabilly Swing Dresses
review_headline: Fun and flirty with a very fitted waist
review_body:
After reading the other reviews about this running a bit small, I ordered a size up. I normally wear a medium and sometimes a small, but ordered a large. The dress feels like a heavy quality material in the hand, but does not feel heavy when on. The large fits me just about perfectly in the waist and I probably would not have been able to zip it if I had gone with my normal size of medium as it is very fitted through the waist, though the neckline does gap. If I pull the cap sleeves off the shoulder a bit, then it fits almost right in the bodice, though the bust could still be a bit snugger even with that adjustment. The skirt is nice and flouncy. It just feels like a fun dress when it's on. It is very comfortable and the material is heavy enough that it cannot be seen through, so a slip is unnecessary. This is a fun and flirty little dress that is reminiscent of Audrey Hepburn's style, and I will enjoy wearing it out for dinner. I received this dress at a promotional price of approximately 50% off for the purpose of product testing and feedback in the form of an honest review.

I try very hard to write reviews that contain information that I would want to know when considering purchasing a product and that I would find helpful in making a purchasing decision. I believe reviews should be honest regardless of whether an item was received free, at a discount, or purchased at full price. I am not affiliated in any way with any company or product for which I leave a review, nor am I compensated in any way for leaving a product review, and a positive review is never guaranteed, only an honest one.

review_body: My daughter loves retro clothes, so I'm always looking for affordable vintage-style clothing for her. My daughter had been looking at both this dress and another similar dress for an upcoming event, so I was quite happy to get a discount on it and provide feedback.  Based upon the other reviews, I went ahead and purchased a size larger for her than she would normally wear. She normally wears either a size 6 or a size 8 depending on the fit of the dress. The large fit her perfectly.  This dress looks classy and the gauze hem adds a touch of elegance. The hidden zipper gives a polished look to the back of the dress. The high quality fabric with durable seams and even stitching makes the dress feel like a more expensive dress. If you're ever shopped for retro/vintage dresses, you know that can get a bit pricey. It's nice to have an affordable line of vintage clothing for those who are on a budget.  I like that this dress is machine washable as I'm not a big fan of having to get clothing dry cleaned.
