review_body:
Very cute. Darker in person, but personally I like it better in real life. The only weird thing is that it is long in the front and short in the back. It fits very nicely and I'm a US size M. The material is nice and soft. This item is delicate, so launder carefully.
1. Do not over wear.
2. Do not over wash.
3. Hand wash, or wash on a delicate cycle. If your washer doesn't have a delicate cycle, just do a short/cold cycle.
4. Air dry, or use a no/low heat cycle in the dryer. But the best option would be to air dry if you are able.

product_title: Cutiefox® Women's Summer Side Slit Casual Beach Mini T Shirt Dresses
review_headline: How You Choose Your Size Should Be How You Want It To Fit
review_body:
Let me address the sizing thing. Use the sizing chart! I got a medium, I'm 130-135lbs 5'3" measurements are 36-26-38. It fits like a tunic and not like a dress as shown but that's what I wanted, a tunic shirt to wear with leggings. It fits more like the picture of the model in lime green for reference. If you want it to fit more like a dress you will need to go two sizes up. It came faster than expected. The tie-dyed pattern is more like a leopard print which was fine, but not correct. I think the material is good and the price is great. I recommend this product, but choose your size how you want it to fit.

Shorthand Version: If you use the sizing chart solely, it will fit like a tunic. If you want it to fit like a dress, use the sizing chart, and go 2 sizes up.

product_title: Great Soles Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Sock
review_headline: Great soles Half Toe Grip Yoga socks - for yoga and more!
review_body:
These are the best yoga socks I have owned. It is the first 1/2 toe design and I wasn't sure if I would like them. I love them!
I don't like bulky socks on my feet but I was concerned about slipping on the floor when attempting to maintain proper form in yoga.

The first attempt to put them on my feet was comical. From the big toe on down each little piggy went into the opening until the little toe. I needed to coax him into line with the rest. I wear size 10 and they stretched to fit. Once the socks were on they were so comfortable even between the toes.

I like all the non slip dots on the bottom, more dots on the bottom than some I have tried. There is extra protection in the back heel area. Once they are on they stay in place. I like the trendy colors especially the ombre effect on the Dusk color. Very stylish.

My 96 year old Mother saw them and wanted to try them on. She uses the non slip socks but hates them. Well, once she tried them on I can't get them back. She calls them her sexy socks! So, Great soles, looks like I'll be ordering some more!

I like that a portion of the proceeds of the sale goes to benefit melanoma and cancer research.

I received this product at a discount in exchange for a honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Great Soles Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Sock
review_body:
Socks with grip bottoms like this are hard to find, and they are often very expensive just for one pair. These are a good deal. I like the fact that they come up slightly over the ankle. The rubber-like grip design on the bottom is also bigger than on a lot of socks of this type; there's one big area in the front and one on the heel. I put mine in the washer and dryer (turned inside out with the rubber-like design on the inside) and they came out fine. Even if you don't do yoga or pilates, they are great for walking around the house on linoleum and wood floors, so you won't slip. They would make a nice little gift for women who are senior citizens, to prevent falls at home. I may order another set later.
I received this product at a discount in exchange for my honest unbiased opinion.

product_title: Great Soles Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Sock
review_headline: These are my second pair of yoga socks and my favorite.
review_body: These are my second pair of yoga socks and my favorite. I kickbox and shoes are not allowed on the mat but socks are. I've tried socks but the slipping and sliding became dangerous. These are perfect. The grip on the soles of the feet are awesome and the toes being cut out helps with grip as well as allow the feet the breath. I like the fact that it is not a full sock for me. It just covers my heel and I don't have a problem with the socks sliding off and the "tongue" aids in pulling the sock up and rests right in the bend of my ankle. The sock is light weight and I wasn't bothered with them while I was working out. Aesthetically, the ombre pattern is nice and gives it a punch of style.  I have washed them once and did not have a problem with shrinkage nor did they fall apart. Altogether, this is a great sock to work out in whenever you don't quite want to be barefoot.  I received this product at a reduced price for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Great Soles Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Sock
review_headline: Better than the Mary jane styles
review_body: Very nice. Only downfall is after 1 hour or so of practice, the toes go numb due to separators. I'm sure this is something you could get used to.

product_title: Great Soles Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Sock
review_body: These are very comfortable yoga socks. I have started using these socks instead of regular socks when doing yoga for two main reasons. The first is the grips on the bottom. Having that helps me not slip on the wooden floors. I feel myself concentrating more since i dont have to worry about falling. The second is the fact that my toes are not in the socks. It feels so much better being able to point easier and move my toes. In regular socks i sometime get my feet itchy if they are dry too. These will officially be my new yoga socks. They have them in several colors too. I chose black just out of personal prefrence knowing they would match with any outfit. I recieved this product at a discounted rate for my honest and unbiased opinion.

product_title: Great Soles Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Sock
review_headline: Fit Comfortably, Useful for Yoga Poses
review_body: I'm just getting into yoga so these were a little treat to myself. They're really comfortable and made of nice, soft fabric. It fit my toes nicely and it was easy to get each little piggy into its own opening. They fit as I expected and aren't too large or too tight, but comfortable and just snug enough that they aren't quitters (socks whose elastic dies long before the fabric itself so they're falling down all the time). These are a nice addition to my fitness routine now that I have them! I received this product at a reduced price in exchange for honest review.

product_title: Great Soles Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Sock
review_headline: The Great Soles socks are what is definitely needed when doing ...
review_body: Extremely comfy socks. The Great Soles socks are what is definitely needed when doing Pilates or yoga. The grip dots the socks have on the sole allow for a better stance. I enjoy the open toes. It makes it easier and I have more wiggle room vs. closed toed socks. The Great Sole socks are a good proper fit. They are light weight and hold their shape after washing. Another reason I love these socks is because I have used them to help with my dry heals. I live in the desert and it's difficult to keep your feet looking descent. So instead of spending lots of money on pedicures and lotions, I use good old Vaseline. Every other night I apply Vaseline to my heels and wear the Great Soles socks to bed. In the morning my heels look perfect. No signs of dry cracking skin. The open toes allow for my feet to breathe. These socks are just what I needed to not have to pay for my own pampering as well as a good workout. I received the Great Soles socks at a discounted price in return for my honest, unbiased review.

product_title: Great Soles Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Sock
review_body:
These are a very comfortable pair of yoga socks. They are perfect for everyday use as well. They are perfect if you like to stretch out as I do. I have tile throughout a portion of my house and the grips on the bottom of the socks help with not slipping. The toe opening is perfect for your your toes to grasp the floor when you are doing moves that might be slippery if you did not have the toe contact with the floor.

I think that they are extremely comfortable and are great for everyday use. I like to have these on when I am just hanging out at home watching a movie.

I received this product at a discount in exchange for my unbiased review of the product. The opinions of the product are based on my experience with and use of the product.

product_title: Great Soles Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Sock
review_headline: Cute non slip yoga socks! These work AWESOME!
review_body: These socks are really comfortable for use in yoga and stretching. I hate it when my feet slip on the mat! This solves the problem and the rubber grip dots are really useful!  Nice to wear around the house since I don't care for slippers.  I ordered the purple design and they're adorable.  I've gotten some compliments on them in class too!  I'm going to order a pair for my yoga instructor as a gift as well.  I order a lot of fitness items on Amazon and I was THRILLED to receive these yoga socks at a discounted price in exchange for an honest and unbiased review.  I'm also really pleased that purchasing these socks also helps with a donation towards cancer research!  I love to support businesses that give back to worthy causes with a portion of proceeds.

product_title: Great Soles Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Sock
review_headline: Great fit, love how they feel
review_body:
I love these Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Socks from Great Soles. This is the first time I have ordered or worn these type of socks and I fell in love. They fit perfectly, love the Purple, the grips on the bottom do not bother my feet at all. I have had other socks that have grips on the bottom and as soon as I had them on and put pressure on my feet it felt like knives going into my feet. Well, I don't even notice they are there with this product. When I wear them around the house my feet do not slip and slide on our hardwood floors, my toes being out help them grip the floor. I find myself wearing them all the time around the house. Normally wearing socks my feet get hot but I guess with these since my toes are out I don't have that problem anymore. Thank goodness..

More about the socks:
Fabric Content: 75% Cotton | 23% Nylon | 2% Elastane
Tread Color: Light Grey
Sock Height: Ankle Cut with Raised Tab Back
Size: One Size (comfortably fits shoe sizes 6 - 10)
Care: Machine wash cold water. Machine dry inside out

I received this product at a discounted price in exchange for an honest and unbiased review. I also want to put this out there that just because I may receive and item for FREE or at a DISCOUNTED PRICE, doesn't mean that I just give it a high rating and made up review. I always try any product or service I get before I give my review. It wouldn't be fair to the Seller nor anyone else who is out there reading reviews to see if they want to purchase it or not.

product_title: Great Soles Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Sock
review_body: I am in love with my new yoga socks.  I have a bit of a fatter foot and have tried others and they fit way too snug, these are perfect.  I like that they are half toe and allow your toes to breath.  The fit is nice and not constricting.  I received the purple ones and they are such a pretty purple and the lower half are black.  These also have the non slip grips on the bottom so when i use them on our hardwood floors i am not sliding around or do not hurt myself.  They are made of a nice breathable material that is not too thick to where you feel like your feet are too hot (one thing i hate the most HOT FEET).  I would recommend these to all my friends that do Yoga or are looking to start, as well as those that just want a good pair of non slip socks.  I received these free for my honest unbiased review.

product_title: Great Soles Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Sock
review_headline: No toe socks, make me able to wear socks again!!
review_body:
I am not a sock person. I am not real fond of closed to shoes either. I hate having anything on my toes, it makes them feel closed in too tight. I know these socks say yoga socks, but I figure I would try them out. I like the way they fit my foot. I love the way my toes are free in them. Having no toes makes me feel like I could wear socks again. I have been searching for something to wear as a replacement for normal footwear. I love that I have found this product.

Another great feature, is the non-skid souls on them. Non skid, grip, whatever you call them - it helps you to not slip and slide on hard wood floors.

I am not a yoga person, so I cannot review how well they work for their intended purpose. But for those of us, whom are hot natured now due to mother nature ... these are wonderful. I did receive this product at a discount in exchange for my review.

product_title: Great Soles Women's Half Toe Grip Yoga Sock
review_headline: What a great concept. I actually think they would be cool ...
review_body:
What a great concept. I actually think they would be cool to wear to bed to keep my feet warm but not too warm. I don't think the quality high end and the price is a little too high but they are comfy. Just have to get used to wearing them. I've been wearing them around the house. I love the no slip soles. Since my floor is slippery at times, these will come in handy.
I also wear them to bed when I want to put lotion on my feet to keep them moisturized. Have the open toes keeps my feet from getting too hot.
I'm going to try taking a yoga class next month, so I'm sure these will be perfect to use. They fit well on my feet and the toe insert holes fit good too.
I received this product at a discount for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Women's Long Sleeve Jersey Knit Striped Comfy Bodycon Dress USA
review_headline: Perfect for fall with a pair of leggings
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:bb5797a629f136d9f2a087c349b68a0d]]This dress is adorable! But if you are on the taller side or have wider shoulders, make sure you order up a size from what you would usually wear. It will help you with the length and make it less clingy. I'm six feet tall and while the dress isn't technically too short to wear (it covered everything it needs to) it was too short for my comfort so I'll need to wear it with leggings. Which is fine because with fall coming up, it is the perfect season for leggings.
The dress is pretty form fitting. It was clingy which would normally not be a big issue, but having recently had twins, the dress showed more of me than I would usually like. That being said, with spanx or other shapewear, it would have evened everything out.
The dress itself is really comfortable. the stretchy material is soft and even though it is a bit thicker, it isn't too hot. Overall, a really cute dress that I look forward to wearing.
I received this product at a discounted price in exchange for my honest and unbiased opinion and review.

review_body:
This dress fits perfectly. I was concerned that it might be too tight for my body but it fits perfectly. As far as my size goes, I ordered an XL. I don't know my measurements in inches but I can say that I am a DDD up top and I wear a size 14 in bottoms. I hope that will help in someone else's ordering decision. I know how hard it can be to find plus sized clothes that actually fit well and flatter your body at the same time. The dress itself is very soft and very comfortable! I didn't want to take it off! I actually felt confident in my dress and that rarely happens in dresses. The material is stretchy and breathable. Even with the long sleeves, it was a thin enough material that I wasn't burning up in the 90 degree summer heat. I paired my dress with my favorite heels but the dress can be worn with just plain flip flops! I ordered mine in black and I love it. I would highly recommend purchasing this bodycon dress!

I like the tiered style of the top & how it flares through both the tiers under the bust area. It's great for me as it helps me cover up my extra weight sitting on my stomach. product_title: Womens Short Sleeve Baby Doll Ruffle Tunic Plus Shirt Top USA
review_body: I've always liked the look of a panel shirt but I didn't think it would look good on me. I'm glad I took a chance on this one because it looks great! Here is why I love this pretty shirt: *Whether you are taller or shorter, it's the style that will look good no mater where the length falls. *I don't love short sleeves, and long sleeves are usually too warm for me. The three quarter sleeves on this top are just right. They do not feel confining , they lay on my arms loosely. *The material is soft and not too thin. I wore this shirt on a very hot and humid day and I was very comfortable. It's a shirt that I will wear all year around. *It's the type of material that can be rolled up and packed and not show wrinkles when unrolled.  *The neckline is very flattering, It does not show cleavage, but it doesn't choke you either. *The color is so pretty, I got the purple. *I've hand washed it twice and it hasn't faded at all. *It's very feminine and girly. *I love that it is made in the USA! If you like the look of the panel style, I think you should give this shirt a chance. I bet you will be as pleasantly surprised as I was! I received this product at a discounted price in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Womens Short Sleeve Baby Doll Ruffle Tunic Plus Shirt Top USA
review_body: This is a really cute shirt. The color is so bright and cheerful and true to what color it looked to be online.  I like having long sleeve or 3/4 sleeve shirts for work because my arms get cold with the air conditioner blowing on me all day. This shirt is light weight and even though it was in the 90s here, it did not bother me that I had a 3/4 sleeve shirt on outside when I was on my lunch break. The shirt is long enough to fully cover my stomach and I don't have to worry about my pouch hanging out when I stretch to get files off the top shelves at work. I love that such a cute shirt can be made in larger sizes, usually the cute shirts are too short and show my stomach or are WAY too small for me even though they say they are plus size. I love how the different panels on this shirt make me look skinnier than I am, it accentuates what curves I have much better than other shirts - especially those that just want to hang like a pillow case on me. I received this product at a discounted price in exchange for my honest and unbiased review. All thoughts and opinions are my own.

product_title: Womens Short Sleeve Baby Doll Ruffle Tunic Plus Shirt Top USA

review_body: This is a really pretty top.  I especially loved this particular color being a true teal when I saw it in person.  I was a little disappointed that they didn't have my size.  However,  my mother who has recently lost a lot of weight and not feeling well needed some new clothes.  She hasn't been up to shopping and I knew after seeing this that she would love this top so I got it for her. She really likes to have some type of sleeve rather than a sleeves top so this one was perfect as it is a 3/4 sleeve.  The material is very soft and lightweight and the stitching is very neatly done and even. The design of the blouse is very flattering and flowy and she said it is very comfortable. She also really liked the way the neckline was cut, sort of rounded and not real deep.  I also think that it will work whether her weight should go up or down a few pounds.  We were grateful to receive this product for free during a promotion in exchange for our honest and unbiased review.

I am a plus-sized woman, and I know how hard it is to find clothes that fit just right. I was looking for some shirts, since my husband is tired of seeing me in his old tee-shirts. When I found the Poshsquare Women's Fashion Colors Paneled Three Quarter Knit Tee Top, I decided to try it out. It arrived very quickly, and I could not wait to try it on. It has a scoop neckline that accents the shirt beautifully. I love the 3/4 length sleeves too! I wore this to my mom's birthday party, and received so many compliments. product_title: Womens Short Sleeve Baby Doll Ruffle Tunic Plus Shirt Top USA
review_body: I got this shirt on the nice green color to go with some pants I own with almost the same shade, This is a very lightweight fabric and I use it here in Hawaii where is really hot , specially now in the summer days. I like the details of the drapes which makes it flowy and makes me very comfortable under it, being an oversized woman I always look for things that are flattering. It sits nice on your body, the sleeves are comfortable as well and I do have chubby arms. The stiches are all straight and well done and I have people ask me where did I get it all the time. I like the neck cut which gives e open chest but not too revealing, looks great with a long chain necklace. You can go from casual to chic with this same shirt in a heartbeat. Great quality materials and assembly. I did order it through a promotion to try it and share my honest opinion and will gladly pay full price for another one or two in other colors!

product_title: Womens Short Sleeve Baby Doll Ruffle Tunic Plus Shirt Top USA
review_headline: while pretty see-through, is definitely great
review_body: The shirt, while pretty see-through, is definitely great. Just throw a cami under it and you're good to go. Unless, you are comfortable with people seeing your skin. The softness of this shirt is wonderful, makes it very comfortable to wear, even bare skinned. We all know how some shirts can be itchy and uncomfortable, this is definitely not one of them. The slight ruffled section of this top is flattery to heavier set women because it makes them look less thick, at least it does me. The one thing I have to say though, is that this top makes your chest look bigger and your stomach look smaller. I love the three quarter sleeves because this top is better for Fall which is mainly what I need clothes for. I am glad I was given the opportunity to receive this top for a discounted price in exchange for my honest and unbiased review. All opinions are 100% my own.

product_title: Womens Short Sleeve Baby Doll Ruffle Tunic Plus Shirt Top USA
review_body: The color of this garment is true to photographed color. I ordered the teal and it's super soft and comfy. However, it is VERY see through which is why I gave it a 4 star. I still really like it though. It does run a bit small for a 1X/XL since I generally wear a size M/L and it fits me more like a bigger L would, not a 1X. So I recommend sizing up if you normally wear plus sizes. I love it as a tunic though with leggings though and think it is one of the most comfortable feeling fabrics I have felt in a while. The construction is great. Perfect seams and not a loose thread in sight. I did receive this product at a discounted rate for my unbiased review, but my opinions are 100% my own. I never guarantee a positive review, only one the product deserves!

product_title: Womens Short Sleeve Baby Doll Ruffle Tunic Plus Shirt Top USA
review_headline: Comfortable , lightweight and great for any size woman.
review_body:
I have recently gained weight due to hormonal problems and am not very comfortable in my own skin, but this top is lovely and makes me feel good in it. It's made of a sheer rayon/spandex and at first glance, I thought I would need to wear a cami under it, but after I put it on, you cannot see thru it. The fabric is so lightweight that you can barely even tell you have it on. lol. I wear about a 16 right now and the XX gives me more than enough room. I probably could have worn a size smaller, but my mind always tells me that I need a bigger size. At almost 5'6 , the bottom of it hits me a little closer to mid thigh than the picture shows...which I like because I feel comfortable wearing it with stretchy, long shorts or leggings underneath. The tiers on the bottom half hang loosely away from my hips, but not so it sticks out. The stitching is always very important to me (that's why I took a pic of it) , and it's all very even with no fraying or loose threads. This material is very thin and fragile, so I suggest washing it by hand and air drying to keep it looking as good as it does now. I got the black , but it also comes in purple and teal. Really thinking about getting the purple one now that I know how much I like it. This will look nice on any size, but I would not go larger than you need in this one. It seems to hang better when the top is more fitted. I wouldn't be worried about getting it too small (as long as you are in your size range) because it has so much "give" to the fabric. You will be as pleased with this top as I am.
I received this top free in exchange for my honest opinion of the product. Very happy that I was given that opportunity to find a top that I love.

product_title: Womens Short Sleeve Baby Doll Ruffle Tunic Plus Shirt Top USA
review_body:
I'm 5'10 and currently 6 months pregnant, and this shirt in a size XL fits perfectly. (I usually wear a large, but went up a size given my current "expanded" state). The drape of the panels on the bottom of the shirt are very flattering, and while it's still obvious that I'm expecting while wearing this shirt, I believe it'll do a lovely job of camouflaging my post-partum tummy in a few months. The bottom of the shirt hits me at hip length (though it should be mentioned that I have a shorter torso for my height).
The material is very lightweight and breathable (97% rayon and 3% spandex) so it's comfortable to wear even on a warm sunny day. It does appear rather sheer at first glance (before you put it on), but happily it's not see through once it's on. I did wear a camisole underneath the shirt just in case, but even outside in direct light you can't see the camisole through the material of the shirt. It's labeled hand wash and line dry. You're also not supposed to iron it, but it doesn't seem to wrinkle (and I don't iron anyway). The material has a bit of stretch to it (the neckline does not, however), which makes for a very comfortable fit. The scoop neck is cut low enough to be flattering, but not so low as to be considered revealing. The quality of the shirt is top notch – well-stitched, no loose threads, no weird gaps or folds.
I received this product at a discount in exchange for my honest review; all opinions are my own.

product_title: Womens Short Sleeve Baby Doll Ruffle Tunic Plus Shirt Top USA
review_body:
This has got to be one of the most soft and genuinely most comfortable shirts/blouses that I have ever worn. It so amazing on too. I did take some pictures in it with my phone but they did not come out too well and I did not have someone with me to take the picture for me. LOL. I should have used a selfie stick to take them.

My daughters have boughten a lot of shirts made out of this material. They claim how soft this material is and how comfortable they are. I myself had never tried one on until now. All I can say is WOW! Now I know what all the fuss is about. It is just so amazingly smooth and soft and feels great against your skin.

The sizing I found to be true to size for me. This fit me perfectly.

It also comes in a huge cloth bag that I will be putting to very good use. The bag is perfect to take shopping with you so you can put in all your purchases.

review_body:
This is an adorable top that will go with lots of different bottoms. This knit top would look great with pants or skirts. It’s made with 97% Rayon and 3% Spandex. The material is very soft and thin. This is a sheer top and you can see through it. I prefer wearing a tank underneath it.

The top has a low scoop neck. I love the ¾ sleeves to hide my huge arms. The flowy bottom is great to hide your belly. It’s also fairly long and will cover your hips.

Measurements for 1X

Bust: 19” across

Waist: 21” across

Hips: 27” across

Arm Length: 11” across

Arm Width: 6” wide

These are approximate measurements while lying flat. This material does have a great amount of stretch to it.

This is a great knit top to wear casual or dress up. You can wear with jeans and flats or dress up with some gorgeous jewelry and a skirt or palazzo pants. This top is very versatile. Is super comfortable and great for the hot summer days. I received this product at a discount in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Womens Short Sleeve Baby Doll Ruffle Tunic Plus Shirt Top USA
review_body:
Womens Fashion Colors Paneled Three Quarter Knit Top
I absolutely love this top because it is really hard to find good looking tops in plus size that you truly like and that fit nicely.
The material on this top is light so it will keep you cool on a nice warm day, but I would suggest to wear something under this top because it is see through so when I wore it I also wore a black tank top underneath to keep from everyone seeing the bra I was wearing.
The stitching on this shirt is done very nicely and I found no loose threading at all.
I also love how on the bottom of this shirt it flows out so that you do not have a tight bottom and it really makes for a fashionable shirt that you could wear just about any where, and would look good with any kind of pants from jeans to khakis.
I received this product in exchange for an honest and unbiased review

product_title: Womens Short sleeve Solid Print Baby Doll Ruffle Tunic Plus Size Top USA PUR 2XL
review_body: There are some days when you don't want to wear anything too fashionable or gawky but just want something really comfortable and easy on your body. I love its bold purple color and 3/4 sleeves. The scoop neck and paneled design makes you appear slim. This knit top is made of thin breathable fabric.This has a very relaxed fit which is a great feature I like about this top. This is a very versatile top as it goes well with shorts or long pants. I love this top, it is so good for this summer. I received this knit tee top at a discount price for an unbiased review.

review_headline: A nice and flowey paneled shirt for the plus sized lady!
review_body: This paneled t-shirt with three quarter sleeves is made from a nice light weight sheer knit fabric that is very nice and flowey. Instead of hugging every curve it just flows right over them and helps camouflage them instead of drawing attention to them which is something I really like. This shirt is on the thin side so I choose to wear a cami or tank with it but that is just my personal choice. I love the paneling on this shirt and it gives the shirt a very roomy feel. I ordered it in teal and I am very happy with my choice. I received this product at a discount in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

review_body:
I've never tried completely hidden socks before these, but I've seen them in the past. As a Converse low top/Vans wearer who lives in a rather warm southern area of the US (95-105 Fahrenheit summers), foot sweat is the bane of my existence. I go sockless in the spring and fall, no problem, but it's not an option in the summer.
Fresh out of the mail, I pulled a pair out of the envelope, threw them on, put on my Vans, and I no longer looked like a grandpa with long socks. The fit was perfect (size 12-13 men's), they kept my feet dry and my shoes absent of any stank.

GUYS WHO WEAR NO SOCKS WITH LOW CUT SHOES, get these and quit having stank feet.

GUYS WHO WEAR LONG SOCKS WITH LOW CUT SHOES, get these and just stop- doing whatever that is..

Shipping: The shipping is China Post. I've ordered many items from China and they can sometimes take a few weeks to several months to land in your mailbox. HOWEVER, this seller worked some kind of black magic and made it to my mailbox in LESS THAN A WEEK!

Cust Support: Top notch, makes sure everything went well.

Quality: Consistent, A++, very well made, they stay on while running and walking up multi-storey car park stairs.

review_headline: This retro bathing suit is absolutely wonderful! Usually when I buy a one piece it's ...
review_body: This retro bathing suit is absolutely wonderful! Usually when I buy a one piece it's either perfect on the top and too big or too little on the bottom or too big or too small on the top perfect on the bottom but not this one It fits perfect everywhere! I bought it in a large in the black with white polkadot, I am 5'3 106lbs, with 36c's.  I love how it's straight back but kind of scrunched in the front. The straps that go around my neck are comfortable and do not irritate or chafe my skin. The leg holes fit my legs just right as some other bathing suits I have had do not have as much stretch as this bathing suit does in that area which can be painful and annoying.  It doesn't stretch so much that it sags when it's wet either and I love that because a saggy butt is not cute! I would recommend this to anyone who loves pin up style clothing like I do.  These are absolutely my very own honest opinions after having received and tried this product for free in exchange for an unbiased and honest review.

product_title: Meaneor Women's Leopard Batwing Sleeve Loose Fit Irregular Hi Lo Top Tunic Tee
review_headline: Can be worn in a formal and informal setting
review_body:
Sent to me for review, this product is presented in a modern, hard plastic resealable bag.

It's made of good quality cotton blend and polyester and whilst one side is thin, the other side is average thickness. As a whole though it's medium weight.

The design is modern and safari (on the back) and I personally found this to be very appealing. It has a v neck with 3/4 length sleeves.

What I liked about this was the loose nature of the top and I found that it was less likely to show those bumps. I also liked the length of the sleeves along with the prominent print as it has really good detailing.

I found that this was suitable for both formal and informal settings so it could be worn in both work and partying for example.

It goes really well with jeans, leggings, crops and skirts with colours such as black, blue or tan.

The fit was really good and I was more than happy with it.

review_body:
This is a very nice, high quality chiffon tank.

I love how detailed the starfish look on this tank top, you can tell that they are starfish and it gives this a top a very summery feel.

The seams on here are also sewed straight and with no snags, which is something I always pay attention to as you can tell how good a clothing item is by this item alone, and this one hits the mark!

I ordered this in an XL as these are Asian sizes and run a bit smaller than our sizing, and I wanted to be on the safe side ( I am a Medium in U.S. Sizing), if I would have ordered a Large it would have been the perfect fit as the XL is a tad too big, so as long as you order a size up you will be fine.

I received this product in exchange for my
honest, unbiased review.

product_title: Mordenmiss Women's Casual Linen Harem Pants with Pockets US 6-8
review_headline: I'm giving these 5 stars because they are beautifully made. I'm am leaving this review specifically to ...
review_body: Even though they did not fit me, I'm giving these 5 stars because they are beautifully made.  I'm am leaving this review specifically to help out potential buyers.  IF you want these to be "big, loose and flowy" like on the model, I wouldn't suggest you order these IF you are over a size US 8.  The reason being that even though the waist stretches to 37 inches, the cut seems a little bit narrower at the top, not good for BIG hips (mine).  When these didn't fit me I had my size 12 daughter try them, and they were snug on her as well.  SO I wouldn't suggest over a size US 8 on this one.  Hopefully that will help avoid "ordering mistakes". :-D  But yeah.  I LOVE them.  I just wish I could wear them!  I did talk with the company and gave them measurements for "average US figures", and the said they would be manufacturing larger versions.  Their customer service is impeccable.

product_title: AkiDress Elegant Lace Bodice with Tulle Skirt Flower Girl Dress for Little Girl
review_body: The dress is pretty, and came nicely pressed with the bows looking perfect, we ordered a size 8 for my daughter who wears a six normally, and size fours for her cousins who usually wear 2T based off of the previous review and they were right, these fit only a bit loose. We ordered them so we can have them altered to fit perfectly for a wedding. Had I ordered their size they normally wear they would have been perhaps even too small.  The color we bought (champagne) is beautiful, and we added a pettiskirt underneath for a bit more fullness. The fabric for the skirt and under portion of the bodice feels a bit thin and fragile, I hope it can hold up to three little girls without any of the dresses ripping on the wedding day. I would expect better quality fabric for the price, and also the lace is as the previous review mentioned, it isn't scalloped, it is straight across, which was also kind of a let down.

review_headline: Still cute, but not exactly as pictured, and runs smaller than chart.
review_body:

I was expecting (based on the measurement chart) that I was going to have to have this dress altered to fit my daughter correctly, instead it fits pretty much perfectly. Great for me, but not so great if you are expecting it to run like the size chart provided. It fits considerably slimmer! (And yes, I am referring to the chart provided by the manufacturer in the pictures.)

Quality is somewhat mediocre. The sewing could be better. It will be fine for my daughter to wear for one day for a wedding.

Overall, it is a cute dress, but I do wish it was as pictured. That, the quality, and the inconsistency of fit (although it was favorable for me, it might not be for others) prevent me from rating it any higher.

review_body: This is just fabulous.  Absolutely gorgeous!  I've always wanted a masquerade mask, there is just something so elegant, stunning and sexy about being in one. The diamond accents add so much elegance and sparkle.  I am so happy that this mask is made of a malleable metal which allows you to adjust it to fit your specific facial structure. review_body: I have to start off by saying that this Masquerade Mask is beautiful. I received the black one but there is a couple of colors for you to choose from. It is made from 100% metal fiber, has beautiful diamond looking rhinestones on it, has two ribbons on it that tie in the back, and is laser cut. The mask is about  8.25" x 3" inches, is delicate, and I was able to bend it easily to fit my face. With the mask being so delicate you really need to be careful when bending it so that you don't break it. This mask is great for masquerade balls, parties, proms, Halloween and more. I myself put mine on my wall to use as a decoration because it is so beautiful. My Mother saw it and fell in love with it so I will be buying some more of these soon to give out as gifts. I received this product as a sample to test and review. This review is solely my opinion. The information provided is what I experienced.

review_headline: Got this dress for my daughter and she loves it, very light weight and comfortable.
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:dbc6a1707061dbbd7a5f7c74abc6e134]]I got this dress for my daughter (back to school time). She is 10 but she is tall for her age so this actually fit her very well; I just had her add a tank top underneath which I thought was a good look anyway. We also dressed it up with a statement necklace to make her feel fancy and she loves it. She loves this dress so much that I had to yell at her to take it off and save it for school because she wants to wear it all the time.

This is very light weight and on the verge of see through (see the video I have included) so a tank top under it is not a bad idea. However, that being said because of the weight of this it is the perfect summer dress; I could see how someone would love to spend all day in this. It has an asymmetrical hem and the front and the back are longer than the sides which gives it a little more visual interest.

No matter what it seems to be a fairly well made, comfortable dress that is great for a variety of ages.

I received this discounted product for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: TL Women's Sleeveless Loose Fit Scoop Neck Tunic Flare Hem Top Tank Mini Dress
review_headline: Extremely Comfortable Woman's Sleeveless Loose Fit Scoop Neck Tunic Dress!
review_body:
I ordered the size Small and this TL Women's Sleeveless Loose Fit Scoop Neck Tunic Dress fit my 5'3" 119 lb frame perfectly.
The Fabric is Ultra Soft, High Quality 95% Rayon / 5% Spandex and the Color is Beautiful!
Top Legging calls it "Blush", but it reminds me of the color of a fresh cut, ripe cantaloupe.
I love that the Cut of the Arm Hole is such that I do not have to worry about the sides of my slip or bra showing, as often happens with Scoop Neck styled, sleeveless clothing because of my short stature.
I also appreciate the flow of this tunic dress style. I am a woman in her early 60's and I have a little bit of a "matronly pooch" in the belly area, which this dress does a nice job of camouflaging.
It is Lightweight, Extremely Comfortable and offers Nice Movement.
The Seams are Well Stitched and the Stitching is Straight and Even Throughout the entire garment. This lovely dress offers a 1/2" Bottom Hem that is Double Row Stitched so it won't easily come undone.
There is a Center Seam down the Back of this dress, however, it is not very noticeable when I have it on due to the overall style and cut.
Care Instructions Read: Hand Wash Cold - Do Not Bleach - Hang/Flat Dry - Dry Cleaning Recommended.
I have yet to wash it, but my guess is that hand washing and hang drying will be sufficient.
It does tend to wrinkle and was wrinkled from being packaged in a plastic bag, however the wrinkles came out easily using my Fabric Steamer.
This garment is Made in the USA, a feature is a Big Plus in my book.
What I did Not care for where this dress is concerned is the Thinness of the fabric. I would not feel at all comfortable wearing it without a decent bra and/or a slip. (It would, however make an extremely attractive bathing suit cover-up)
While the cut and extra fabric around the mid-line will hide my belly, those portions of this dress where the fabric lies flush against the skin, will Not hide even the slightest bump or bulge.
In fact, the nature of this fabric, combined with the thinner material tends to accentuate them and for that reason I am only giving it a 4 Star rating.
I am posting photos, but as I had no one available to help shoot them, 2 of them were shot while the dress was on a hanger and the sides were taped to the wall to show the width and cut of the bottom of the dress.
Top Legging shipped quickly and I received my dress 2 days earlier than expected.
I received this dress at a promotional price in exchange for testing and providing my honest and unbiased review.
Well deserving of my 4 Star Recommendation.ill Not hide even the slightest bump or bulge.

product_title: Womens Stretch Printed Leggings
review_body: I received the small/medium womens stretch printed leggings in Aztec.  These are really pretty leggings,  and they fit wonderfully.  At about a size 5 these fit perfectly.  They breathe really well,  and they don't stretch out at days end like others do.  These are super comfortable and very soft to the touch.  They are made from a poly/spandex blend and stretch to fit any body type. They don't bunch up while you are wearing them.  You can pair these leggings with many tops,  and washing them is easy,  just hand wash with cold water and lay flat to dry.  I recieved these at a discount for my honest review and I would recommend these to anyone who wants some leggings that are super comfortable and super cute.

product_title: Womens Stretch Printed Leggings
review_body:
These leggings are great. I love the design and they are a perfect match for almost any top.
They are very well made of high quality fabric.
I love leggings and these are super comfortable.
They should be hand washed and laid flat to dry to prevent damage to the product.
I received this product at a discount for an unbiased review.

product_title: Womens Stretch Printed Leggings
review_body: I love clothes and shopping and right now I'm really into fun prints and colors.  I thought these would make a perfect addition to my wardrobe.  I'm currently 2 months postpartum and my clothes "fit" but not the same way.  When I pulled these leggings on, I was beyond elated that the material, quality, and look of them are perfect!  They are extremely comfortable and feel like a second skin.  They are lightweight and the perfect fit.  I normally wear a Large and the Large fit me perfectly.  They weren't tight or uncomfortable like some leggings are, especially at the waist.  Not only are the leggings extremely comfortable, they're extremely well made.  Being a lightweight fabric, sometimes stitching and craftsmanship can be less than average.  That was definitely not the case with these leggings.  The seams are stitched well, no strings or loose seams anywhere on there and no signs of that happening after two washes.  I love the Aztec print on the leggings and the unique fun patterns.  I paired them with a solid black tunic tank and some black wedges.  I also wore colorful jewelry and a matching clutch for a pop of color.  I love finding a fun way to dress up and be comfortable.  It can also be worn as a more casual look with flip flops and a long shirt.  Promotional discount provided in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Womens Stretch Printed Leggings
review_headline: Our package arrived quickly and in perfect condition. These leggings were even nicer than I ...
review_body:
I purchased these Aztec print leggings in black and white for my 11 year old daughter. She is quite shapely and we ordered a size small. Our package arrived quickly and in perfect condition. These leggings were even nicer than I had anticipated and were very well made, the material very nice, not cheap at all and VERY soft. I was quite impressed with the quality of the work on these pants, the stitches are tight, no loose strings and these seem like they are going to hold up very well and for quite a long time. They fit perfectly and were just the right amount of snugness and feel that these fit exactly as I had anticipated. I really love them and love that they go with so many tops! Great deal!

I purchased this product at a discount price and have provided my honest and unbiased review in return.

review_body:
If anyone has ordered Asian bikinis, they know the sizing. I am 5'8" 140lbs and usually wear medium/34C at VS. Don't follow the generic Amazon size chart. I got a large in this bikini. The bottoms are a bit tight, but not that bad. The top is good - It doesn't feel snug but it's a pretty good fit.

The bikini is EXACTLY like the picture. Pretty skimpy in the back but not as bad as the picture shows. The top is lightly padded, but it's removable. Colors and material are great!

I haven't gotten to wear it yet, but I'm SUPER excited to! Very unique so it'll definitely draw attention.

5 stars because it's exactly what I expected. A lot of the lower ratings come from sizing, but that is something you should be aware of before ordering Asian bikinis!

product_title: S-noilite 23 inch Orange Hair Cosplay Wig Long Curly Hair Heat Resistant Synthetic Hair Halloween Anime Costume Wig Full Wigs
review_headline: This isn't even the same wig as the picture, it's pinkish orange, not a fox red, or copper red at all.
review_body:
Probably the only positive about this wig is that it isn't super shiny like some inexpensive wigs are. But sadly it does not resemble the photo at all, especially if you need that exact color wig for a cosplay. The picture makes the wig look more of like an auburn color or a fox red, with small brown undertones. That is not the case at all for this wig.
This wig is just like clay pot orange, or like a burnt orange. I needed this wig for my Dark Phoenix cosplay and I thought wow this is the perfect color..it is not. The wig also does not sit beautifully like this, it sits more blunt in my opinion, kind of straight across. I posted a picture in hopes that it helps anyone, and don't mind my face I was sending it to my cosplay group and was making a confused face.
The wig is thick, it isn't bad quality but it just isn't what was pictured. It's so orange and it has kind of a pink hue to it. I gave it 2 stars because for the price but that is it. You couldn't even say that my screen colors were off because the cut isn't even the same.

I tried to return it and of course I would have to pay for postage and the wig was $11 so it's not worth it, I am stuck with this wig.

product_title: Brave Person Men's Professional design Running Tights Stretch Shorts
review_headline: If you have abs, these will look great on you
review_body:
These are good looking "football" pants. If you've read other reviews, you'll notice that these pants are made with a loose weave, that lets you see thru the material. There is a piece of orange cloth, that passes in front of your privates. So you don't wear these commando style. Or, maybe you do, but I don't. I have a pair of those 95% cotton, 5% spandex sports underwear, in black. So these football pants look fine worn over those form fitting cotton/spandex underwear. Plus, you maintain your modesty, if that's what you want to call it. Don't wear whitie tighties with these, you'd look wrong. Now, a word about how these fit. These are form fitting. The legs stop below my knees, and then hug my body up to my waist. I'm still a little flabby around the waist, (subcutaneous fat) so these don't look that great on me. If you have big thighs from heavy squats, the material will stretch to fit what you got. (I suppose up to a point, that is.) These XL fit like a large, but a large that might run 34" to 36", or POSSIBLY 35" to 37". As for who would look good with these, I'd have to say, a man with a trim, athletic, or even muscular build, with a body fat level of 10% or less. If you can see your abs, or you don't have flab, then yes, you could wear these. Just get the right size, and make sure you have some form fitting cotton-spandex underwear, in a color that works with the pants. (like black.) Hey, if you put that many hours a week in the gym, and are that serious with your diet, then you DESERVE to wear these pants. I have another 5 to 10 pounds of fat to lose before I look good in these, but hey, now I have a goal, right?
A free sample was provided to me, in exchange for a fair and honest review.

product_title: Brave Person Men's Professional design Running Tights Stretch Shorts
review_headline: My adult son would probably give them a 5 but as his mom I think they could be more modest
review_body:
Free product provided for evaluation and review.
I received the Dark Blue pair in the Asian XL. They have red side panels.

These fit my adult teen son who normally wears a waist size 36 or men's large, so they fit as expected.
They are a stretchy mesh, and they have 'holes' all in them from the mesh, so up close they are quite see through. From a distance, it is hard to tell and they just look blue. They have a red small piece in the front as a modesty panel for the family jewels, but the jewels were still sparkling a bit. It would be nicer if that panel were larger. There's nothing modest about these.

My son did find them incredibly comfortable and cool though, and good for working out. They really cling to the buttocks and show off muscles. They are stretchy and very nonbinding. They stay up well. He keeps wearing them for workouts, because I am washing them pretty often. They are holding up well in the wash and there has been no shrinkage or fading at all, they still look great.

The downside is that they probably are too revealing for more modest guys.

product_title: Women's Bright Color Neoprene Padded Swimwear Top & Bottom(sky_blue,large)
review_body:
This is a very cool bikini made out of the same material as a wet suit (neoprene); I've never seen such a thing until I got this. At first I was wondering if it was going to be comfortable because it appears stiff but I put it on and felt it was very comfortable. I've been wearing the top a lot under different tank tops. (I often wear bathing suit tops in the summer underneath different tops since they often show a little bit.) It's supportive and hold you up nicely, and the back has a flat clip so there are no strings to create a bulge under your shirt. The straps are detachable and can be removed for a strapless top. There's some removable pads that create a push-up effect. I love how the pads are secured well so they won't slide around. Since this is made of neoprene it also dries pretty quickly. I've washed it in the washing machine and air dried it and it looks perfect still. I'm very happy with it!

(Swim suit provided free for testing and honest, unbiased review.)

product_title: Slim Wallet - Minimalist Front Pocket Wallet - Leather Money Clip Wallet Card Holders RFID Blocking
review_headline: Minimalist wallet that allows for growth if needed. Excellent for use in front or back pockets. Design has attention to detail.
review_body:
This review is for the MEKU Leather Credit Card Holder.

This wallet has a very smart design. It has six card pockets, two larger card / receipt pockets and one large slip in the middle for your cash.

At first inspection I didn't think this wallet could hold that much, I was wrong. It's designed in a way that gives you a lot of storage but removes all the unneeded material. The best way to describe it is two credit card holders sewn up to create an area to store cash folded over.

For me this wallet is right in-between a minimalist and regular wallet. It really is a minimalist wallet in size if you fill it light but it does have the option to grow to a more normal size if necessary.

Advice:
If you are new to having a smaller wallet I have some advice. If you have a smartphone there are apps that will let you digitize your loyalty cards, some phones can even be scanned. You can also create an all in one bar code card online which could cut out 8 or so cards from you wallet.

I was provided this product in exchange for my honest review.

product_title: Slim Wallet - Minimalist Front Pocket Wallet - Leather Money Clip Wallet Card Holders RFID Blocking
review_headline: Nice, light well-made wallet for your front pocket
review_body: Exactly as described.  Unlike other wallets I've purchased over the years, this wallet has nice straight stitching and well-tailored leather components. The wallet is much lighter in weight than I expected, even with six cards in the pockets, cash in the middle and business cards in the remaining two pockets. Fits nicely in the front pockets of shorts and trousers.  One caveat, though, is that this wallet will not hold a lot of cash in the center compartment without it becoming rather bulky.  I regularly have no more than 8-10 bills at a time and that's about all it can hold to keep its slim profile.

product_title: Slim Wallet - Minimalist Front Pocket Wallet - Leather Money Clip Wallet Card Holders RFID Blocking
review_body: Nice, thin credit card case that isn't bulky like so many are! It only holds 6 cards; the spaces are a bit too tight to slide more than one card in each. Real leather and it comes in three colors. I love mine!

product_title: Buttons & Pleats Advanced Type Shirt Stays Durable with Non-slip Locking Clamps
review_headline: Good product that doesn't poke holes in your shirts
review_body:
I've tried a couple different brands of shirt stays over the years. If you wear dress shirts and want to look neat and professional all day, you need these to keep your shirt tucked in. I have used another brand for a couple years that had good clamps but they put holes in my shirts and the material would eventually begin to tear at the hole.
These do a great job of holding the shirts but so not poke holes like the other brand.
I'm not really a fan of the adjustment buckles since I'm over six feet tall and don't need them. I imagine shorter guys may find them useful. The quality of the clamps on these shirt stays seems to be very good and I am pleased with their performance.

review_body: I know these are made for men but my son loves these he uses them for our shabbat service and even for school nerd days. I know it's not anything fancy but they do work completely keeping the shirt in place and the pants pulled up instead of finding a belt. They are easy to adjust. The clips are easy to place on the pants and easy to take off as well. I recieved this product for free to review and give my unbiased opinion and review.

product_title: Buttons & Pleats Advanced Type Shirt Stays Durable with Non-slip Locking Clamps
review_headline: Great concept and works as expected, personally not much comfortable for me
review_body:
I am sure this is a common problem with most males that their shirt does not stay tucked in the whole day. Earlier I used to get my trousers stitched and I used to have a rubber sea across the entire circumference of the trousers in the inside. That would help me keep my shirt tucked in all the time. But now with all readymade trousers / pants, I don’t really have that option.

I found this shirt stays by accident and got it at once to see how I can make use of this to keep my shirts tucked in. The do work as advertised. The listing has 3 different types of shirt tucks available and you can buy the one you think best works for you. I got the Y shaped one as the one where 2 straps would be in inside area of the legs was a not so comfortable idea for me.
The way you are supposed to wear this is that, the end with one strap attaches to your sock on one leg and the other end with 2 straps attach to your shirt on the same leg.

There is an adjuster in between so you can change the length of strap but the strap by itself is elastic. Let me straight get to the comfort part. Initially, you will feel something bothering is there running through almost entire length of your legs. This is expected as I am sure no one is used to wearing such a thing. In fact you will be very conscious all the time at work or on road that are people aware you are wearing it or is it not showing through the trouser. This shirt tucker does the work as advertised for sure, how comfortable you are with this the entire day is based on person to person. You can check all designs and see whatever you think you will like best.

The grip system on this which holds your shirt or sock has a plastic piece in between and is made in such a way that it won’t mess with your shirts so you can be assured that your shirts or socks won’t tear or anything. The elastic strap does not cause any irritation on skin but you will always have a feeling that “something” is thereand may take few days or couple of weeks to get adjusted to that feeling.
Overall it is a great product and works as expected, just that for me the feeling was too bothersome and I may not be using it much unless on special occasions. I am planning to use this to keep my fitted sheets proper on my mattress. I am not sure if you have noticed but those sheet holder also appear almost same.
*I received this product in exchange of a honest and unbiased review and all my opinions mentioned above are based on my experience of using this product.

product_title: Buttons & Pleats Advanced Type Shirt Stays Durable with Non-slip Locking Clamps
review_body:
I don't know about anyone else but for some reason whenever my shirt gets all pulled out and wrinkly I get so damn self conscious thinking the whole room's eyes are are on me even though logically I know nobody really cares. I would always excuse myself to the bathroom every hour or two to readjust my dress shirt to make sure it was nice and tucked in. Nothing ruins my confidence more than looking sloppy. Eventually I decided to google some methods on how to keep my shirt nicely tucked in throughout a long day and the most common answer I found was to use a shirt stay. I then discovered the Buttons and Pleats Shirt Stays and after using them for a few days I have to say I am absolutely in love with these things! Ever after a long day of constant movement my shirt stayed nice and tucked in and I didn't have excuse myself to the bathroom to readjust my shirt once! This was a huge confidence booster and time saver for me. I purchased the Y strap option and it worked amazing, I just attach one hook from each leg to the back of my dress shirt and the other to the sides of my dress s*** and make sure there is a firm grip. I can't believe I didn't use a shirt stay sooner but now that I have discovered them, I don't think I'll ever put on a dress shirt (unless it's a casual one) without them again.

Please note I received this item at a discounted rate for my honest and unbiased review.

review_headline: Well made, very soft V-neck toddler shirts
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:9169a080434fc43d4be2bc4f9bb7cdda]]I love when my son wears a v-neck and these are no exception. I was just going to do some photos of him in these but he insisted on doing a video review. :-)

These are very soft shirts and like all the vaenait baby products I have they are very well made. I got my son a 4T which I think fits him very well. He is tall and skinny and that is how these shirts are made. They seem tight when we first put them on him but they don't seem tight at all once they are on. There is a tag on the front of each on of them on the bottom that says, \\"I don't chase boys I run past them\\". I'm not sure how I feel about this tag but I can say I would love to see this printed in large print on a girl's shirt. :-)

I'm not sure if these will shrink in the wash because I washed these and then dried them out on the line but if they do shrink I will update this review. It is hard to tell because the care instructions are not written in English which would be helpful.

Overall, I really like the look and quality of these shirts. Of course I think my son looks cute in anything but he even likes this shirt except for the \\" wet one\\" (mommy didn't get the one completely dry before doing the review). :-)

I received this complimentary product for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Xuerry Women Sleeveless Bodycon Lace Chiffon Cocktail Party Prom Dresses 2XL pink
review_headline: Super cute dress! Great value for a good price!
review_body:
This dress is a great value for the price! The quality of the material is actually better than I expected, and the color is pretty true to the photo. The fit is pretty accurate from what I can tell... I am on the downhill of a weight loss adventure and ordered a size smaller than I would have a few weeks ago thinking that it would be tight, and was pleasantly surprised that it fit well. I love the light weight of the fabric, it feels very "floaty" against my skin which is always a gamble with lace as it can sometimes be very scratchy. This dress seems well-made, for the price point, and while I am confidant in saying that I will also mention that (as a seamstress) there are two TINY things that bothered me. There were loose serge strings on the inside that I trimmed up before I tried it on, not a big deal at all and has no impact on my opinion of the dress, but if you have long nails check before putting this on so you don't catch a nail on a string. The second thing is the band around the waist is only tacked on with one spot in the front center, and once on each side seam. This felt very loose to me before trying it on, however it had no impact on the way the band sat against the dress once it was on, and is attached well against the zipper so there is no chance that it would fall off! Overall this dress is a GREAT value for the price, and looks wonderful on! Very cute party dress!

I received this item at a discounted rate in exchange for my honest and unbiased review!

product_title: Meaneor Women's High Waist Wide Leg Boho Chic Palazzo Lounge Pant Loose Trousers
review_headline: Stylish, versatile pant that you can dress up or down.  Comfy!  *UPDATED REVIEW*
review_body:
I'm a person all about comfort with style and these wide leg pants were exactly what I was looking for. You can dress them up with your favorite blouse and heels/boots for the office or a night on the town, or you can dress them down with a nice t-shirt or workout jacket for a walk in the park or a trip to the gym. They're made of a very soft, thin fabric blend and are matte in color, not shiny.

When I first opened the package and held the pants up for inspection, I was worried because they looked too small. However, I pulled them on easily and the fit is almost perfect and are so comfortable. NOTE - these pants are made in China and the sizing is smaller than western sizes, so you might want to order these a size or two larger than what you would normally wear if you're accustomed to pant sizes in the US. The length seems good, if perhaps a little long. I'm 5'6" and these pants are a little too long when wearing tennis shoes, but fit perfectly when I'm wearing boots or heels.

I do have a couple of minor issues, though. On me, the crotch area rides a little high. Also, the narrow elastic band at the top of the pant cuts into my stomach just a little when sitting. If the elastic was a bit wider, this probably wouldn't be an issue, but as it is, it kind of feels like a tiny rope around my waist. On the plus side of that, I don't think these pants are likely to slip and fall down on their own, which is a problem I've had with other stretchy pants. Overall, these are a nice, stylish, versatile pant that you can wear for any occasion. Recommended.

UPDATE 9/25/15 - I am changing my review from 5 stars to 2 stars because after just a few weeks of occasional light wear and a handful of washings, a large tear has already appeared in the seat of these pants. On closer inspection, the stitching at the seams is very flimsy and not durable. Although these pants are stylish, the durability is very questionable. I would not recommend this product.up in the material of the opposite leg when you're walking and trip yourself. This is especially true if they fit long on you. I have had this happen with another pair of wide leg pants and it resulted in a nasty fall. I almost had this happen to me last night while wearing these particular pants, so it is something to think about when deciding whether to purchase this garment or not. I don't think I'm a particularly clumsy walker, but I do tend to walk quickly and take long strides, so perhaps getting tripped up in the leg fabric is an issue that not everyone will encounter. I love the wide leg look though, so I'll take the chance.

Overall, these are a nice, stylish, versatile pant that you can wear for any occasion. Recommended.

product_title: Meaneor Women's High Waist Wide Leg Boho Chic Palazzo Lounge Pant Loose Trousers
review_headline: bell-bottom style comfy pants with extra long legs
review_body: I was kindly provided with a reviewer's sample of this product for honest reviewing purposes:  * About the material: The product description describes it as a "cotton blend" - to the touch it feels like the "blend" part is the dominantly obvious part. It feels very silky and has a bit of stretch to it - my guess it's blended with maybe polyester, lycra, bamboo-fibre or spandex, or a mix of some of these together. The fabric is thin and light, and feels nice, sleek and comfortable on the skin.  * About the sizing: I ordered the XXL size, going by the waist and hip measurements in the product description. Important Note: XXL in Chinese sizes is much, much smaller than XXLs in American sizes.  - Waist & Hips sizing: I found the hip and waist sizing to be accurate to the measurements given on the product page, and these were a comfortable fit. I liked that the trousers have an elasticated waist that can adjust to fit you comfortably. The XXL was a good fit for me (I'm usually a medium size in Western sizes) - if your size is usually much bigger than Western large-sizes, the waist may be a little tight on you. I recommend double-checking the waist and hip measurements they give in the product description before ordering.  - Leg length: For me, these trousers were maybe 15cm too long. I'm only 5'3 (around 160cm tall) so maybe if you're a taller lady (say about 170-175cm, or taller than 5'6), these pants may be a better fit on you. Alternatively, if you're happy cutting and hemming the bottoms, I guess you could adjust these to fit even if they are a little long straight out of the box.  - Leg width: I'm not sure if this is because I ordered the XXL, but the pant leg width was really, really wide (like 46cm wide) - like bell-bottoms. Baggy and loose the lower down you go.  * About the stitching: The waistband area had some loose threads but other than that the stitching elsewhere looked good.  * Overall: If you're a tall lady, looking for wide-bottomed comfy trousers, are happy with the material being a silky-feeling blend, these trousers may be a good choice for you.

product_title: Zxzy Galaxy Print Crop Tank Top/Pleated Skater Skirts Set For Women
review_body:
I received this product for free or highly discounted in exchange for my honest review.

To start off, I really like the pattern of my crop top and skirt combo. I got the galaxy one, the one with Van Gogh's Starry Night as the skirt. I thought the pattern was super cute, and I am glad I picked that one. Beyond the pattern, I really do not like this set, but I do not hate it either. It is just OK. The material is really thin and cheap, and while it does have some stretch, it is somewhat small. I am 5'9" with long torso and legs and broader shoulders, and the top was a little tight on me on the arms, and the skirt, well I'll need to be careful how I wear it. I do not think I can wash this, just hand-wash, but I am not even sure if I would wear it. The material is not comfortable at all, but I guess at the price it is, I am not terrible surprised. I wish I could say it was worth it, but this product was not really worth the discounted price let alone the actual price. I wanted to like this combo, but I really can't. If you are petite, going to a rave or concert where you need cheap but cute outfits,and do not mind cheap fabric this would be ideal but beyond that no deal for me.

Overall, I do not recommend this product.

review_headline: Not great for those larger than an A-cup...
review_body: I wanted to love these. I'm a 34B and judging from the pictures (of obviously not small-chested models) and the positive reviews by other B-cup and even C-cup women I was assuming these would work fine. They are too small. I wanted wireless comfort, modesty pads, and a v-neckline to help avoid that sports bra shape. The "cup" of the bra doesn't cover as much width as a standard bra cup - as you can see in the side shots of the models. The unfortunate result of this for me was a double side-boob. Not very attractive. I ended up gifting them to my younger (and smaller) sisters. I'm going to guess that part of the issue could be that I'm not the same shape or *ahem* firmness that I used to be before nursing 2 babies. The search for the perfect bra continues...

product_title: Just Love Women's Black Scrub Pants / Scrubs
review_body: I am not a medical or dental professional so I am not required to wear scrubs to my job.  I ordered these because I am always impressed by how well scrubs can withstand to a variety of tasks, chemicals, liquids, etc.  I am a mom of two humans and two canines and I am always cleaning up, hosing down, washing off, wiping, rinsing, scrubbing ... something or someone.  Instead of messing up my good clothes I decided that scrubs are the way to go.  Now, I can't claim I came up with this idea on my own, it was actually a former daycare provider of mine who would wear scrubs each and every day during daycare hours simply because they hold up for the very reasons I listed above.  This pair of pants will need some softener in the wash as you can tell they are new but the fit and length is perfect.  I will definitely be purchasing more!  I received these at a discount in exchange for my honest review.

product_title: Just Love Women's Black Scrub Pants / Scrubs
review_headline: Great pair of functional scrub pants!
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:3c3ca659bc2bc76a5e5f2bdbb3359415]]This review is for the Just Love Women's Black Scrub Pant - Extra Large.

I LOVE these XL scrub pants from Just Love! I am a size 14/16 and I am 5'8 in height and they fit me PERFECTLY! The waist features high quality elastic and easily pulls up and down when putting them on or taking them off for the night. They are super comfortable to bend and twist during my shift at the hospital with patients. The best part is the length. I am 5'8 and need REALLY long legs! These legs must be approx a 33 inch inseam as they DO NOT FLOOD ON me and actually cover my ankles and tops of shoes! I LOVE THAT because it is extremely hard for me to find pants that are the perfect length.

The pants are SUPER SOFT and the material washes well and steams well. I am a nut and always steam my scrubs after every wash. I like to look professional and wrinkle free on the hospital floor with patients; it gives them a better impression. I always hang dry my garments also, so if you plan to put these in the dryer I am not 100% sure on their outcome for you with shrinkage, but I know these DO NOT SHRINK when you machine wash cold and air dry.

I also love these pants as the pockets are well placed. There is a side pocket that fits my stethoscope perfectly. It is deep enough that my steth has no worry of dropping out. The top has two slant pockets and I carry my personal items in their depths. (Tampons, pads, and cash). These pants are slightly baggy but provide enough shape that they aren't too casual looking. Very nice black color goes with all the scrub tops I own also.

5/5 stars for materials, design and functionality.

If you have any questions please post below and I would be happy to answer! I received a free promotional sample of this item for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Zxzy Galaxy Girls Digital Print Stretchy Flared Pleated Casual Mini Skirt
review_body: My daughter love this ! She is 10 and it fits her very well. The material is so nice and strechy it will last her a long time. We got the adventure time print. She wants to wear it everyday if I would let her.  This did take about 2 weeks to arrive. I did receive this at a discount for my honest review.

product_title: Zxzy Galaxy Girls Digital Print Stretchy Flared Pleated Casual Mini Skirt
review_body:
This skirt is so cute I couldn't help but get it for my daughter. The Adventure Time characters and bright, bold colors made this a perfect addition to her school wardrobe. With the color variety on this, you have so many different options to wear with it too.

The skirt is long enough to be worn for school and looks great with tights or leggings. The stretchy, breathable material allows it to fit comfortably and provides flexibility in sizing too. This says one size and we received skirt marked XL. My daughter and her friend wear sizes 8-10, both tried this on and this was a little big on them. I would say it is a girls size 12-14 comfortably. It is soft and silky and the cotton blend material flows around you as you walk. This material will snag though if you aren't careful, so I wouldn't suggest this for wood benches, hiking, carnival rides or anywhere that you might sit on something that could rip it.

I love this skirt and would purchase some of the other color options too. It is fun, flashy and a unique piece that will stand out in a crowd. My daughter loves that she will be the only one at school wearing this once we have it adjusted to fit her better. It will work alone now, and layered for cooler weather, and with the stretch, it will fit her for awhile too. It's a win!

*I received a small discount on this product in exchange for an honest review. All opinions are my own.

product_title: Zxzy Galaxy Girls Digital Print Stretchy Flared Pleated Casual Mini Skirt
review_body:

product_title: Zxzy Galaxy Women's Sexy Strap Crop Top Plant Printed Tank Tops Blouse Vest
review_body:
I received this product for free or highly discounted in exchange for my honest review.

I have always wanted a crop top, and when I saw this, I thought I would get a really cute and comfy looking one. To start, I got the chevron one, and I really do like the pattern; however, it is a thin material and white, so a nude or white bra is a must. The material, as I said, is thin and cheap. I am a tactile person, so I really do not like the feel of it. It is a little itchy and just uncomfortable. It is not cotton I can tell you that. The material gives some stretch, but even then, this top is somewhat small and tight. I am 5'9" with a long torso and broader shoulders, so it was a little tight for me around the arms. It was OK on the torso because I also have a small bust line, so one size fits all shirts tend to fit because they counteract each other. I really wanted to like this top, but I really cannot, but I cannot hate it either. If I ever need something cute and cheap to wear at like a concert or party or something, I would think about wearing it, but it is not for everyday use. If you have a need for it in that capacity as well and are petite with a small chest like I do (36A,) then I think you would do OK.

As a note, my sister tried this top on because she loved chevron, and it did not cover her at all! She is a couple inches shorter than me, but she is a D cup. It barely got over her nipples even with the small stretch the fabric gave.

Overall, I do not recommend this product.

review_headline: That innocence and beautiful look of white.
review_body:
During my inspection of the waist trainer I found no loose strings, holes or buttons.

The entire waist trainer is covered in a beautiful, bright white silky material with a beautiful light floral design on it. The trainer comes together in the from with 5 very well made, heavy duty metal buttons and hooks. On the back of this beautiful trainer is a gorgeous white, silk ribbon that allows you to loosen and tighten the garment.

Also running along the sides and back I found support lines with a strong yet flexible material. These support lines serve to help hold those hard to train parts of the tummy and waist area in place.

The trainer also came with a very cute thong that coordinates with the trainer perfectly.

Over all I would say that this trainer is very elegant, well made and perfect for everyday wear, wast training or those special nights with a special someone.
